or: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562719656684810.jpg\" title=\"1562719656684810.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a></p>',1,0,50,'1562719672','旅途掠影',1,12,25,127),(50,'郏县广阔天地大有作为纪念馆','/uploads/20190710/328bfd4ebe6617288d98e17b2cf9f0e2.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">广阔天地大有作为纪念馆位于河南省平顶山市郏县广阔天地乡。该馆是全国首家知青主题纪念馆，也是郏县知青园景区的重要组成部分。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562720717355098.jpg\" alt=\"纪念馆全景\" title=\"纪念馆全景\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">新馆在2012年12月24日开馆。纪念馆占地38亩，建筑面积3000平方米，布展面积2700平方米，总投资3000万元。主要内容包括序厅、广阔天地缘起、广阔天地纪实、广阔天地洗礼、广阔天地瞭望、多媒体沙盘厅、临展厅、贵宾厅、多媒体厅等组成。旨在通过对历史的真实展现，给人们以启迪、给青年以激励、给研究者以借鉴，它将成为全国最大的知青资料中心，研究知青文化中心。该馆在布展上以纪念毛泽东主席批示为主题，以“广阔天地、大有作为”为主线，展出上千幅图片。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562720717216659.jpg\" alt=\"纪念馆序厅\" title=\"纪念馆序厅\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">纪念馆在2013年被评为河南省爱国主义教育基地，同时还是平顶山市党员干部现代远程教育工作示范基地、平顶山市党员干部现代远程教育教学培训基地，接待游客28万余人，举行各种教育活动25余次。广阔天地大有作为纪念馆是平顶山学院、许昌学院等周边大中专院校的教育实践基地，这将对知青文化的发展和知青精神的宣传发挥更大的作用。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562720718358171.jpg\" alt=\"馆内雕塑\" title=\"馆内雕塑\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">日常开展活动</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"></span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"></strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">1.纪念馆基本陈列&nbsp;2.纪念馆临时陈列</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562720807160969.jpg\" title=\"1562720807160969.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a></p>',1,1,50,'1562720850','旅途掠影',8,12,20,94),(51,'程庄村传统民居','/uploads/20190710/be5454bd74c350208181af5fb5e1855f.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">程庄村传统民居位于平顶山市宝丰县李庄乡程庄村，西临贺窑村，西北距全国重点文物保护单位父城遗址1.5公里，东临郏县李口乡，村域面积1.6平方公里。大清同治五年（1866年）散兵土匪打家劫舍，为防匪患，全村人搬石挖壕建成一座石寨，故名为“同协寨”。现石寨已毁，寨壕仍存。程庄村的传统建筑和村落格局记录了从明代以来程庄村发展演变，经济的盛弱、文化的兴替。古建筑群由寨壕围合而成，设寨门和戏台，有护城河环绕，建筑随地形而建。民居整体为合院式，功能分区合理，主次分明，立面高大，装饰精美。建筑形式古朴典雅，各座单体错落有致，互为呼应，规划合理，保留着典型的清代院落布局和建筑特征，集中反映了该地区清代民居建筑的建筑风格和建筑水平。整体建筑布局合理实用，是研究该区域清代中上层家族建筑布局和设计理念的实物资料，具有重要的科学价值。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562721066937343.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">程庄村传统民居以明清和民国时期为主，集中连片分布在村中偏北部，以单层或二层阁楼式的砖石结构为主，其建筑特征是基础与下槛墙以红石垒砌，青砖灰瓦顶式，砖雕和木雕精美别致，保存较好。含程家大院、刘家大院、关帝庙、刘春峰老宅、程家祠堂、刘邦老宅、蒋新老宅、赵宝乾老宅、程广善老宅、程大岭老宅、程明星老宅、程大钦老宅、贺宗军老宅、刘俊义老宅、石拱桥等15处。2013年，程庄村被住建部、文化部、财政部、文物局联合公布为第二批中国传统村落。2016年，程庄村传统民居被省政府公布为第七批省级文物保护单位。</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font face=\"宋体, SimSun\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562721285203880.jpg\" title=\"1562721285203880.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></font></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>',1,0,50,'1562721159','旅途掠影',6,12,25,80),(52,'宝丰县大营村传统民居','/uploads/20190710/40603ce03cd8195cb0ae19757f728afe.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">大营村传统民居位于平顶山市宝丰县大营镇大营村，明至民国。大营镇始于隋唐，毁于元初，明洪武年间（1392年），村镇复。北齐时在此设关驻兵以御北周，因系大本营，故名大营。宋时称青岭镇及兴宝镇，明初为吴、王二寨，清为大营镇至今。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562721552560459.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">大营村传统民居含关帝庙（又称山陕会馆）、吴水旺老宅、王之晋旧居、行老商老宅、苏英臣老宅、樊应仁老宅、杜硕老宅、王栓柱老宅、影壁、王富泰老宅、吴玉庆老宅、赵东方老宅、黄健老宅、赵天星老宅、白衣堂（三村小学旧址）、王文明老宅、郑振林老宅、高铁旦老宅、郭红旗老宅、任莲老宅、王志魁老宅、王香莲老宅、李奇老宅、王玉红老宅、大营人民公社旧址、苏常聚老宅、牛王庙、苏胜利老宅、朱西欣老宅、六村门楼、赵小杰老宅、郭会仁老宅、王士伟老宅、王朝中老宅、石留群老宅、寨壕、国民党军抗日纪念地等37处。建筑集中连片分布于大营一村、二村、四村、六村、南关村，多为明、清、民国时期所建。建筑以单层砖木结构为主，青砖灰瓦顶，木制门窗，建筑布局和式样以北方四合院形式为主，留了历史原状，具有鲜明的地方特色。大营村传统民居整体格局保存状况基本完整，院落轴线关系明晰，各院落主体建筑基本保留历史原构，留存不同时期的历史活动信息，为延续至今或业已消逝的文化或文明提供特殊的佐证。2013年，大营村被住建部、文化部、财政部、文物局联合公布为第二批中国传统村落。2016年，大营村传统民居被省政府公布为第七批省级文物保护单位。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562721620482434.jpg\" title=\"1562721620482434.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>',1,0,50,'1562721657','旅途掠影',18,12,25,77),(53,'商酒务榷酒遗址','/uploads/20190710/13fe90137ba59aacf9b92f6902fa73d6.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">商酒务榷酒遗址位于平顶山市宝丰县商酒务镇商酒务村北，为宋至清代酿酒遗址，面积约30000平方米。商酒务在宋时为宛洛古道要冲，因该地属京西北路，临近京都开封，是著名的酒类制作和集散地。商酒务榷酒遗址内曾发现有烧酒锅灶、古井遗迹及大量钱币、汝瓷、钧瓷、酒坛、鸡腿瓶酒器残片等遗物。遗址大部为农田。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562722461527374.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">据《星野图考》记载：“汝海应野多酒事，仪狄造酒汝海之南，应邑之野，取其水尔” 。春秋时期《世本》载：“仪狄始作酒醪，以变五味”。战国末期《吕氏春秋》在“审分览第五·勿躬”篇里，列举了中国古代二十项创始发明，“仪狄造酒”是其中一项。汉代史书《战国策·魏策》记载：“昔者，帝女命仪狄作酒而美，献之禹，禹饮而甘之，遂疏仪狄，绝旨酒曰‘后世必有以酒亡其国者’”。宋元丰年间（1078～1085年），理学家程颢监商酒务酒税，并留下了“酒务春风”之佳话。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562722462160125.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">该遗址为研究中原酒文化起源发展、榷酒专卖制度建立和古代商业活动提供了有力的佐证。2016年，被省政府公布为第七批省级文物保护单位。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562722568632960.jpg\" title=\"1562722568632960.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a></p>',1,0,50,'1562722616','旅途掠影',8,12,25,78),(54,'塔里赤墓碑','/uploads/20190710/1b44e8c56d55fcf06b38d5e03b2616b6.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">塔里赤墓碑位于河南省平顶山市宝丰县赵庄镇官衙村，元代。坐北朝南，全名为“大元赠辅国上将军浙东道宣慰使元帅护军临汝郡公神道碑铭”，该碑由其子广西道宣慰使都元帅万奴于至治三年（1323年）所立，察罕篆额，宋民望撰文，姜元佐书丹。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562722732164419.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">塔里赤墓碑为青石雕刻，由碑额、碑身和龟趺基础构成，碑额与碑身为一块青石雕刻而成。通高4.1米，宽1.15米，厚0.36米，碑文楷书28行，每行71字，共1988字。首行题曰：“大元赠辅国上将军浙东道宣慰使元帅护军临汝郡公神道碑铭”。碑额为半圆形，额题阴文篆书“大元临汝郡公神道碑铭”10字，围饰二龙戏珠的马蹄形浮雕，龟趺。碑文虽经六个多世纪风雨剥蚀，仍完好无损，清晰可见。周围为基本农田。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562722733922244.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">碑文内容主要记述塔里赤的身世、官历，灭亡南宋，镇压南方农民起义与少数民族反抗斗争的战功，以及生卒年月、宗亲和后裔等。《元史：塔里赤传》虽有记载塔里赤的生卒年月、身世、官史及宗亲后裔，但远不及碑文详尽。碑文记载可补正史《元史•塔里赤传》记述之不足。由于元代初期特殊的墓葬制度，塔里赤墓具体位置不详。1963年，被省人民委员会公布为第一批省级文物保护单位。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562722857869096.jpg\" title=\"1562722857869096.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>',1,0,50,'1562722890','旅途掠影',6,12,25,82),(55,'文笔峰塔','/uploads/20190710/15e1924f91edf4b9af5391d214409449.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">文笔峰塔位于平顶山市宝丰县城南文笔山上，明代。又称文峰塔，创建于明万历四十七年（公元1613年），距今已四百多年。文笔峰塔由射箭台、塔身、碑刻组成。射箭台原台四周青石包砌，面积400平方米，台高2米，台顶四面石栏。相传为东汉胶东候贾复所筑之射箭靶台，故名。清末民国初年，由于战争和人为破坏，周围石砌建筑荡然无存。 1983年7月重新砌筑射箭台。文笔峰塔高12.4米，基围10.8米，为六棱实心砖塔，下有六角青石塔座，上部六棱尖顶，无层、无门窗，略似华表，造型别致，风格独特，为河南省之孤例。塔上方南侧镶嵌碑刻一方，碑文阴刻楷书，主要记述建塔主持人及捐款者姓氏、出身。捐款者有辅佐李自成大顺政权丞相牛金星之名，与香山寺戌辰科状元刘若宰于崇祯三年所撰“重修香山寺观音大士塔记碑”碑阴之“崇祯丁卯举人邑人牛金星”记载相吻合。该塔保存较好，为研究明代建塔技术及传统文化提供了实物资料，具有较高的文物价值。1986年，被省政府公布为第二批省级文物保护单位。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">　</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723029926957.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723074992930.jpg\" title=\"1562723074992930.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p></a></p>',1,0,50,'1562723098','旅途掠影',15,12,25,0),(56,'王忠福泥塑','/uploads/20190710/167bfedb221254f81b4aef84cdf90825.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">泥塑艺术是我国一种古老常见的民间艺术。鲁山县王忠富泥塑，以张扬的造型、大巧似拙的创意、蕴藏的灵性、独具的幽默而引起了许多专家学者的关注。台湾著名诗人出版家痖弦先生看了王忠富的作品说：“王忠富的泥塑作品非常有力，大气。”艺术大师韩美林等人称王忠富的泥塑作品“大拙大美”。王忠富泥塑作品题材多为反映农民劳动生活的场景，创意精美，造型夸张，出神入化，独具灵性，给人以返璞归真的感觉。既是写意，又是“漫塑”充满了浓郁的乡土气息。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723346952178.png\" alt=\"泥塑\" title=\"泥塑\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 591px; height: 313px;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">王忠富泥塑选用带些黏性又细腻的土，选好的泥土还需要加工，要把泥土捻碎、晒干，然后用水泡，再用棒子锤打，像揉面一样揉，有时还要在泥土里加些棉絮、纸，最后还要放置一段时间，泥才有韧性。泥塑先要制子儿。制子儿就是制出原型，找一块和好的泥，运用雕、塑、捏等手法，塑造好一个形象，经过修改、磨光、晾干后即可，有些作品还要用火烧一下，加强强度。整个泥塑过程皆为手工制作，每个泥塑皆独一无二，一线一面展现着憨厚、活泼、质朴的农村生活，同时也体现着民间艺术家的坚韧和智慧。王忠富创作的作品《生活》荣获“河南省首届民间艺术节”金奖；《春播》荣获“北京·中国民间艺术国际展览会”山花奖；《农民》获得“杭州国际民间手工艺品展览会”银奖；《小憩》获得“苏州第二届民间艺术节”金奖；另有多个作品获奖。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">2011年，该项目被列入第三批河南省省级非物质文化遗产名录。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723346696120.png\" alt=\"泥塑1\" title=\"泥塑1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723438516805.jpg\" title=\"1562723438516805.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a></p>',1,0,50,'1562723482','旅途掠影',9,12,22,0),(57,'赵庄魔术','/uploads/20190710/1e2d860d2d351cb0ec3c415d34d930f5.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">赵庄镇周营村农历四月初八有魔术大会；全县有每隔二至三年一届的中国·宝丰魔术文化节。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">赵庄乡位于河南省宝丰县城以北15公里处，踞汝、宝、郏交界之处。是闻名全国的“特色文化之乡”，也是享誉海内外的“魔术之乡”。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723645861457.png\" alt=\"图片1\" title=\"图片1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 555px; height: 271px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">赵庄魔术历史悠久，源远流长，春秋战国时期，这里即有魔王用幻术、魔术护民的传说。该乡魔冢营村建于盛唐时期的“云水寺”，大殿前卷鹏的东西山墙上至今仍有“吃火吐旗杆”“吃针引线”“口吐五彩”等魔术杂耍图案。历经唐、宋、元、明、清及民国，延续至今，1978年后，赵庄魔术获得了更大的发展空间，民间魔术团体如雨后春笋，迅速发展，特别是进入21世纪以来，赵庄魔术的产业化发展势头更加强劲，全乡共有魔术团体632个，从艺人员1.1万人，年创经济收入1.3亿元，同时带动周边乡镇4万余人进入文化产业，并最终促成了“宝丰现象”的形成。这种以非物质文化生产方式分流农村富余劳动力的形式，不仅引起了国内外专家学者的极大关注，而且得到了国家、省领导的充分肯定，国内外媒体相继对其进行报道。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723647887450.png\" alt=\"魔术1\" title=\"魔术1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">赵庄魔术表演节目类型有：手彩魔术，如：“空穴染巾”等；器物人体魔术，如“硬币飞渡”等；气功魔术，如“口吞宝剑”等；创新节目，如“火箭飞人”等。演出形式包括“撩明地”“扎圈子”“大棚”“剧场”等。赵庄魔术在长期的实践中，形成了自己独特的艺术特征：一是它来自民间，又造福于民。二是赵庄魔术使用的道具大多是艺人自己研制的，造价低廉，易于表演。三是广泛的参与性。赵庄魔术现有从艺人员1.1万人，占全乡总人口的1/2。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">赵庄魔术拥有1400多年的发展历史，能够延续至今，本身就是一部民间优秀文化传承的发展史，它以其独特的技艺传承千年，成为绚丽多彩的中国杂技艺术的瑰宝。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">2011年，该项目被入第三批河南省省级非物质文化遗产名录。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723744505568.jpg\" title=\"1562723744505568.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>',1,0,50,'1562723783','旅途掠影',7,12,25,82),(59,'墨子传说','/uploads/20190710/3696c30f8c6d5f38899841072b9cd611.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br/></span></a></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">墨子作为鲁山人，不仅有丰富的遗迹、文物，还有源远流长的民间传说相印证。他们都是鲁山墨子文化的重要组成部分。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723912636741.png\" alt=\"磨子_副本\" title=\"磨子_副本\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">相传墨子出生在鲁山熊背乡竹园村，年轻时在西茅山教授弟子，这期间与鲁班在风筝山比巧，鲁班飞鸢三日不下，墨子木车载荷行动如飞；鲁班又在文殊寺抽取银杏树中心板；二人又在鲁山西南边锤白云山骆驼峰刻石对弈，巨石因名棋盘石。墨子年老时，由于壮志未酬，感人世变幻，就回到故里熊背乡隐居，原姓墨字去掉土，改为黑姓，至今黑隐寺一带有黑姓子孙。所处山沟，因名土掉沟，后人建寺供奉，因名黑隐寺，谐音“黑隐士”。墨子长期居住山洞中，死后葬于附近，山洞即墨子洞。据说墨子晚年归隐鲁山时，意欲著书立说，却找不到一处清雅之地，后鲁阳公得知此事便在金山环岛上为墨子建造了著经阁，那里环境清幽，绿水青山，墨子十分满意，在那里用8年时间完成了《墨子》一书。又说墨子在南天门升仙成道，后来成为道教神仙，在西汉时还有人见过他。墨子与相家有亲戚关系，鲁山相家沟村的相家过去看守尧山镇的墨庙，并是“膛匠班”“成义堂”的倡立者。这些传说体系完整，互相联系，共同组成了墨子在鲁山的生活画面。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562723914568826.png\" alt=\"磨子1_副本1\" title=\"磨子1_副本1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; width: 761px; height: 377px;\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562724033897516.jpg\" title=\"1562724033897516.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></a></p><p><br/></p>',1,0,50,'1562724124','旅途掠影',46,12,22,43),(60,'叶公传说','/uploads/20190710/b046c08215afaa1807c44a35e38b8f87.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">叶公沈诸梁，字子高，春秋楚人，楚昭王时受封于叶，史称叶公。从《左传》、《论语》、《史记》中散见的关于叶公的记载中，可以看出他是当时楚国有一定影响的政治家、军事家、思想家。他曾于公元前479年率军平定了著名的楚国白公胜之乱，在救出楚惠王、稳定楚国政局之后，功成身退，仍回叶邑封地。公元前490年前后，他与著名思想家孔子在叶地进行了以“直躬”为话题的著名政论，他的“直躬”说异于孔子“父为子隐、子为父隐”的儒家思想，但他通过亲身实践，证明自己具有法治色彩的治国理念更有利于兴国安邦。</span></a><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562724278446918.png\" alt=\"叶公\" title=\"叶公\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562724308957251.jpg\" title=\"1562724308957251.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></a></p><p></p>',1,1,50,'1562724346','旅途掠影',52,12,29,129);

