color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" list-style-type:=\"\" padding-inline-start:=\"\" margin-block-start:=\"\" margin-block-end:=\"\" max-width:=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">舞钢龙湖商务酒店建于2013年，是一栋别墅型的建筑，外形似宫殿，设计自然，细细流淌极致之美。那些富有想象力的设计和优雅的细节总让人陶醉，每一处的设施无不彰显环保和尊贵的完美结合。酒店主楼共三层，建筑面积9000多平方米，毗邻石漫滩水库，环境优美，风景怡人，是您旅游度假的首选。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; text-align: center;\" helvetica=\"\" list-style-type:=\"\" padding-inline-start:=\"\" margin-block-start:=\"\" margin-block-end:=\"\" max-width:=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190707/1562469008290746.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" list-style-type:=\"\" padding-inline-start:=\"\" margin-block-start:=\"\" margin-block-end:=\"\" max-width:=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-f