为经营理念，在社会中树立起良好的企业形象。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562894100325912.jpg\" alt=\"图片1\" title=\"图片1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">平顶山锋瑞旅游开发有限公司位于平顶山郏县茨芭三苏园4A级景区附近，成立于2017年9月，注册资金2000万，流转土地1500亩，主要从事旅游资源开发、餐饮住宿服务、文化娱乐服务、特色农业种植、特色农产品销售等。公司秉承生态旅游发展理念，以三苏园为背景，向周边地区以辐射状态建设旅游区。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562894101712976.jpg\" alt=\"图片2\" title=\"图片2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">平顶山锋瑞旅游开发有限公司种植果树1500亩，投资500万平整土地，打井造林，种植桃树三十六个品种，杏李五个品种，从每年的六月份就有仙桃成熟，品种不间断能持续半年以上，园区内空气清新，生态环境良好，生产的果实果型硕大，色泽艳丽，香脆可口，深受消费者青睐。同时，本园区所种植的仙桃经中国绿色发展中心检验合格，成为平顶山首家绿色水果基地。还被评为河南省名优产品，知名农产品等。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562894101574169.jpg\" alt=\"图片11\" title=\"图片11\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">平顶山锋瑞旅游开发有限公司特色餐饮民宿区有民宿单间12个，房间空气清晰，环境良好，可谓是世外桃源，而且餐饮区所有肉食全部来自本园区生态散养，柴鸡、鹅、兔、山羊、黑猪，水塘里还有鲤鱼，草鱼等，餐厅严格管理，制作过程中生熟分开，让客户在这吃的舒心，吃的放心。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562894101501787.jpg\" alt=\"图片13\" title=\"图片13\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562894251479885.jpg\" title=\"1562894251479885.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</p>',1,2,1,50,0.00),(20,'舞钢大酒店','四星级饭店',0,'河南省舞钢市湖滨大道东段 ',' 0375-8116999','/uploads/20190712/60a8a013359f5b55d82f9378749b78ec.jpg','1,2,3,4','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">舞钢大酒店是一座集会议与商务为一体的高档酒店。它位于舞钢市石漫滩水库北岸，地理位置优越，交通便利，四通八达，是舞钢市现今唯一一家四星级酒店。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562894976470228.jpg\" alt=\"舞钢\" title=\"舞钢\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">酒店餐饮以粤菜、川菜和河南风味菜为主，精品佳肴，名厨制作。现有豪华包间16个，餐位600个，可承办各类大型会议和宴会服务。自助餐厅环境优雅，菜品繁多。另有舞钢大酒店美食广场，是您消暑纳凉的必备场所。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562894976686129.jpg\" alt=\"舞钢1\" title=\"舞钢1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">酒店现有客房235间，装饰高雅，设备齐全，温馨舒适。其中包括设施考究、尊贵典雅、具有皇室风范的总统套房；气派、高档、实用的行政商务套房；宽敞、明亮的大床房；经济、舒适的标准间。另有可容纳200人的多功能厅和5个各类中小会议室。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562894977845793.jpg\" alt=\"舞钢2\" title=\"舞钢2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; 