tyle=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">提供WIFI、擦鞋、送餐、洗衣、叫醒等服务</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895056901817.jpg\" title=\"1562895056901817.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>',1,1,1,50,0.00);
INSERT INTO `ddsc_hotel` VALUES (21,'玉京温泉度假酒店','四星级饭店',0,'鲁山县下汤镇 ',' 0375-5668888','/uploads/20190712/a524688b53ebfa0149c74650ab517fe1.jpg','1,2,3,4','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">玉京温泉度假酒店坐落在素有3000年温泉之乡美誉的中州名镇——鲁山县下汤镇，是集温泉养生、餐饮美食、住宿娱乐、商旅会务、拓展训练为一体的四星级综合型温泉主题度假酒店。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895157366428.jpg\" alt=\"玉京3\" title=\"玉京3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">玉京温泉度假酒店温泉出水温度62℃，富含氡、苏打、镁、钠、硫磺及含有大量的硫化物(1mg/L)和一定量的溴化物、碘化物等30余种有益人体健康的矿物质微量元素，PH值为8.85，为弱碱性硫磺泉。硫磺泉的主要保健养生作用有：刺激皮肤引起皮肤血管扩张，改善皮肤血液循环和组织营养，增强抵抗力。具有软化皮肤、溶解角质、灭菌、杀虫等作用，浴后令皮肤更加光滑、富有弹性；可使植物性神经系统兴奋活跃，有较好的镇静、止痛的作用，对神经官能症、植物性神经紊乱等有较好的理疗保健疗效；还能促进关节浸润物的吸收，缓解关节韧带的紧张，改善关节软组织硫质的代谢，恢复功能活动，消除疼痛。对各种关节不适有较好的保健作用；另外还能够改善新陈代谢，因泉水中所含胶状硫磺分子微小，易进入体内组织，起类似触媒作用，使体内的废物由皮肤和肾脏排出体外，积极改善人体新陈代谢。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895157422594.jpg\" alt=\"玉京4\" title=\"玉京4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">客房类型：</strong><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">单间/标间、三人间/圆床套、三人套/普通套房、别墅一层、别墅二层、整栋别墅、豪华别墅</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895158404053.jpg\" alt=\"玉京9\" title=\"玉京9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895158290109.jpg\" alt=\"玉京8\" title=\"玉京8\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">服务项目<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">温泉洗浴、客房住宿、餐饮、娱乐、旅游购物、休闲养生于一体</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895160107829.jpg\" alt=\"玉京5\" title=\"玉京5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><h4 class=\"tit-bar\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-size: 0.373333rem; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">交通指南</span></h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">1、郑州——南四环侯寨收费站上郑尧高速159公里处下汤出口下高速。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">2、许昌——许平南高速至叶县境内转南洛高速至平顶山转郑尧高速159公里处下汤出口下高速。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">3、南阳——二广高速转郑尧高速下汤站出口下高速。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">4、洛阳——二广高速转郑尧高速下汤站出口下高速。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895272393875.jpg\" title=\"1562895272393875.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p><p><br/></p>',1,1,1,50,0.00),(22,'皇姑浴温泉国际酒店','四星级饭店',0,'鲁山县下汤镇 ','0375-5669999','/uploads/20190712/5616fe9a337f3d0f0a6c86c6d57ed00f.jpg','1,2,3,4','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">皇姑浴温泉国际酒店位于有三千多年历史记载的温泉之乡——平顶山市鲁山县下汤镇。西邻尧山和中原大佛景区，东临昭平湖及世界刘氏祖庭。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895475435347.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">二广高速与郑尧高速在此交汇，均设有下汤站口。交通十分便利。我酒店集餐饮、住宿、休闲、会议为一体的园林式温泉主题系列酒店，已被国家旅游局评为四星级酒店。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895476569910.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">有着三千多年历史记载的温泉之乡——平顶山市鲁山县下汤镇，皇姑浴，地泉水质奇佳，清澈柔滑。富含氟、氡、钾、钠、钙、镁、锂、碳等56种对人体有益的矿物质和微量元素，浴之可健体美肤，祛病疗疾。瑶池养生会馆有：男女洗浴大厅、室内游泳池、室外汤池、网吧、休息大厅、影视厅、健身房、乒乓球室、按摩间等服务设施</span>。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895476588828.jpg\" alt=\"5\" title=\"5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895477933040.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">客房类型：</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">标间、单间、套房、单栋别墅、别墅两室一厅</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">服务项目<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">：</span></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">洗浴、住宿、餐饮、会议</span></p><h4 class=\"tit-bar\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-size: 0.373333rem; font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">交通指南</span></h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">（1）平顶山到皇姑浴自驾车路线：平顶山出发，南洛高速-郑尧高速-下汤站下-走下汤环镇路1000m到下汤西头即是，全程30分钟</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">（2）郑州到皇姑浴自驾车路线：郑州出发，郑尧高速-下汤站下-走下汤环镇路1000m到下汤西头即是，全程70分钟</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">（3）许昌到皇姑浴自驾车路线：许昌出发，南兰高速-南洛高速-郑尧高速-下汤站下-走下汤环镇路1000m到下汤西头即是，全程60分钟</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562895576601720.jpg\" title=\"1562895576601720.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>',1,1,1,50,0.00),(23,'龙源大酒店','三星级饭店',0,' 平顶山市新华路南段六号 ',' 0375-3963999','/uploads/20190712/2cb153f9ecdcb1104a4714be5edc446d.jpg','1,2,3,4','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">龙源大酒店于2003年1月8日开业，位于新华路南段，距离火车站1公里，北邻湛河。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562898192766302.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">酒店集餐饮、住宿、会议于一体。酒店餐饮有三百个餐位，可承接各种宴会接待，酒店菜品兼具各种档次，可满足不同消费人群和口味；酒店客房共七十六间，有豪华套房、标准间，房间清洁典雅，配备高档家具和洁具，全天供应热水和空调，每个房间都有高速网络和高清电视。酒店非常重视安全工作，监控已经实现全覆盖，消防设施处于二十四小时自动运行状态，可保证客人放心入住；酒店有大型停车场，有大型绿地和不同品种的树木和鲜花，有自动喷泉和夜景亮化灯光，风景别致优美。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562898193553490.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 17.28px; white-space: nor