aa9.jpg','1,2,3,4','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">中天大酒店地处鲁山县鲁平大道东段，是县城唯一一家集餐饮、住宿、会务、洗浴为一体的三星级酒店。中天大酒店交通便利，地理位置优越，环境幽雅，酒店设施齐全，是您婚宴庆典、宴请宾朋、入住下榻的理想选择。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562898482980046.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">中天大酒店建筑面积8000多平方米，拥有布置豪华的套房、豪华单人间、普通套房、标准间等各类房间。餐饮部经营全国各地的特色菜肴，为您奉献绿色美味的佳肴。健康洁净的洗浴中心，为您冲去一路疲劳。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562898482197421