 font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">好友拼单 人满发货 人不满退款</span></p>',''),(65,35,'拼团分享标题',50,1,'','<p>赶快来吧,就差你一个</p>',''),(66,36,'拼团分享描述',50,1,'','<p>拼团分享描述拼团分享描述拼团分享描述拼团分享描述</p>',''),(68,38,'邀请砍价',50,1,'','<p>邀请好友砍价免费拿门票喽</p>','/uploads/20190711/85d4547dc081c6487a2fecce978bd650.jpg'),(69,39,'banner',50,0,'','','/uploads/20190701/8b579f2777ced00884ba23baf4558a89.png'),(73,6,'河南珍藏的最美瀑布，就在鲁山',50,1,'','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">河南地处中国中部，不像南方那样水资源丰富，所以河南人对水的感情也更亲切，对瀑布也更是情有独钟。在河南很多的山地景区中都有或大或小的瀑布，有的气吞山河，有的细若游丝，有的如悬空中，有的曲折蜿蜒。在这些众多的瀑布中有挂瀑布，在美景的映衬下显得低调了许多。这就是尧山景区的黑龙潭瀑布。</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">尧山黑龙潭瀑布又称九曲瀑布，是尧山国家重点风景名胜区主要瀑布之一，尧山山峰奇特，瀑布众多，森林茂密，大山壁立，异峰如塑，怪石纷呈，是尧山自然风光的一大特色。站立主峰玉皇顶上，千岩万壑，飞龙走凤，远近高低，景色迥异，构成了一幅幅美不尽收的图画。黑龙潭瀑布作为景区的重要景观供游客观赏。</span></p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/4ba72daba2504d32b2409348e29ba98e\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"457\" alt=\"河南珍藏的最美瀑布，就在鲁山\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/8daf329491154049933e04d896b1f01a\" img_width=\"452\" img_height=\"652\" alt=\"河南珍藏的最美瀑布，就在鲁山\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">尧山黑龙潭瀑布高70余米，呈三弯九曲之状，水面根据枯水与丰水期分别宽1-6米不等，由于水流下切磨蚀与岩石承受侵蚀能力不同等因素，断崖上形成数个深度0.3-1.5米不等的凹窝，呈之字形自上而下分布，使壁面凹凸不平，水流形成三弯九曲之状，故也称之为九曲瀑布。</p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/d10138ea10db4f34b4198b9573d41358\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"373\" alt=\"河南珍藏的最美瀑布，就在鲁山\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/89536adf986644159b0e030207f5891c\" img_width=\"600\" img_height=\"401\" alt=\"河南珍藏的最美瀑布，就在鲁山\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">瀑布两边的崖壁上，秀木扶疏，青苔密布，各色野花撒落其间，与雪白的瀑布交相辉映，织成一幅锦绣图案。由于石人山降水丰沛，上游植被繁茂，水源涵养好，瀑水常年不断。瀑布注入下端的黑龙潭，訇响声传出半里之外。</p><p><img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/8083c3aedaf74729babc2639afcc2b59\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"1138\" alt=\"河南珍藏的最美瀑布，就在鲁山\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">每到夏季，山水如兽直扑潭中，九穴则全然不见，留下击鼓撞钟般的吼叫，崩花溅玉，一派雷霆万钧、大气磅礴的壮观景象。平日里，潺潺飞流从穴缘泻下，瀑白穴幽，交相映衬。瀑下潭水清澈透底，涟漪阵阵，碧光闪耀，令人唏嘘。</span><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/7bbadb6e1cac4eeab7928e9b0edef4e8\" img_width=\"640\" img_height=\"427\" alt=\"河南珍藏的最美瀑布，就在鲁山\" inline=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 10px auto;\"/></p><p class=\"pgc-img-caption\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); line-height: 16px;\"><br/></p><p><br/></p>','/uploads/20190627/85bc8b7b610ccc2228946a0346c5b74f.jpg'),(75,2,'心灵故乡  老家河南',50,1,'','<p>心灵故乡&nbsp; 老家河南</p>','/uploads/20190711/588f3b68a293425208717a2e83ae5512.jpg'),(77,2,'心灵故乡  老家河南',50,1,'','<h1 class=\"article-title\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 34px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 44px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">心灵故乡&nbsp; 老家河南</h1><p><br/></p>','/uploads/20190711/e58fe246f89c1bbeb49fc3c35b2ea0c5.jpg'),(80,6,'乡村旅游banner',50,1,'http://xiangyan.dd371.com/index/spot/detail/id/9.html','','/uploads/20190629/663525703475bc4875cd3e048ac7ee8f.jpg'),(81,43,'民宿banner',50,1,'http://xiangyan.dd371.com/index/spot/detail/id/9.html','','/uploads/20190705/d669414d59e1fd1232be597862a53809.jpg'),(82,44,'游记banner',50,1,'http://xiangyan.dd371.com/index/spot/detail/id/9.html','','/uploads/20190705/ff2a102b7249b7a174ac4a57dc9b894a.jpg'),(83,40,'内页砍价banner',50,1,'','','/uploads/20190701/aec48edd8e4b654170ce316df9807911.png'),(85,46,'象眼旅行',50,1,'','','/uploads/20190702/c937fae952201b4a7d4c2cba377767ec.jpg'),(87,4,'资讯中心',50,1,'','','/uploads/20190711/207abbf5f44be37af07cf64d27329ee7.jpg'),(88,45,'美食',50,1,'','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">河南菜又名豫菜,历史悠久,风味独特,早在宋代,就已形成色香味俱全的宫廷风味菜肴。是中国传统美食之一。主要特点是:选料精良、讲究配菜、汤鲜香浓、色形俱佳。河南美食历史悠久口味独特，河南特色美食虽种类多样。河南特色小吃一直是来河南游客心中的那抹回不去的记忆，河南的小吃虽然不贵，但是却有着回味无穷的能量，河南特色小吃还等什么，来河南一定要来品尝这等美食哦!</span></p>','/uploads/20190711/2805d60df12851f1e2585ebb8aa746cd.jpg'),(89,45,'美食',50,1,'','','/uploads/20190711/d7ab6850b3f079c24db0f0ff8fc3fb2d.jpg'),(90,37,'团购抢票',50,1,'','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 57, 57); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">发起拼团低价购票</span></p>','/uploads/20190713/53e48a5cb0f063ffbad8f2515a3954b9.jpg');

#
# Structure for table "ddsc_lb_place"
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `ddsc_lb_place`;
CREATE TABLE `ddsc_lb_place` (
  `pl_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT COMMENT '轮播id',
  `pl_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '位置名称',
  PRIMARY KEY (`pl_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=47 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT COMMENT='广告位';

