 rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">在郑州→嵩山南路→过南四环→上郑尧高速→在尧山出站口下车→沿尧山方向→按尧山景区指示牌行驶→中原大佛景区</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">洛阳、南阳、焦作、济源、三门峡到中原大佛景区的自驾路线:</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">上二广高速沿南阳、襄樊方向(正南)→下汤站转郑尧高速(沿尧山方向)到尧山出站口→按尧山景区指示牌行驶→中原大佛景区</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">安阳、濮阳、新乡、鹤壁到中原大佛景区的自驾路线:</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">京珠高速到漯河→转南洛高速→到平顶山西转郑尧高速(沿尧山方向)→在尧山出站口→按尧山景区指示牌行驶→中原大佛景区</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">陕西省方向到中原大佛景区的自驾路线:</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">连霍高速→(洛阳转)二广高速→(平顶山转)郑尧高速→尧山出站口→按尧山景区指示牌行驶→中原大佛景区。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">山西省到中原大佛景区的自驾路线:</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">上二广高速沿南阳、襄樊方向(正南)→下汤站转郑尧高速→沿尧山方向→到尧山出站口→按尧山景区指示牌行驶→中原大佛景区</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190707/1562495576107951.jpg\" title=\"1562495576107951.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></a></p><p><br/></p>','2,3,4,7',1,'1562495591','平顶山市鲁山县赵村镇上汤村 ',50,1,0.00,0.00),(19,5,0,'平顶山博物馆','舒适','AAAA','周二—周日9:00—17:00，周一闭馆','','','','/uploads/20190708/6f6ed461b81c3ca432262686c00918af.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/443e9b80bc4c04f01ca173d599c35123.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">平顶山博物馆位于长安大道与怀仁路交叉口的平安广场西侧，依地势而立，交通便利；望烟波而居，景色宜人。占地面积54亩，建筑面积3万平方米，是我市投资最多，建筑面积最大的公益性文化设施。该建筑由清华大学建筑设计研究院设计，外形理念源自我国古书竹简的形象，墙体由一片片抽象的竹简构成，造型雄浑大气，古韵盎然，同时也寄寓着博物馆作为文明使者的传播功能。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562577913488291.jpg\" alt=\"677541705572236085\" title=\"677541705572236085\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">馆舍周围绿树成荫，四季常青，三季有花，两季有果；22亩的牡丹园里种有一万七千余株牡丹，包含九大色系，一百六十六个品种。平顶山博物馆隶属于平顶山市文化广电和旅游局，是公益性文化事业单位，内设办公室、安保部、社教部、陈展部、保管部、文物科技保护中心6个部室，现有中心文物库房、“鹰城古韵--平顶山历史与文化陈列和城市规划陈列三大功能，馆藏文物3万余件，3级品以上珍贵文物2000余件。</span></a><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562577914651214.jpg\" alt=\"346498807066480860\" title=\"346498807066480860\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562577914655105.png\" alt=\"17\" title=\"17\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">自2012年5月15日开馆以来，接待社会各界观众400余万人次。先后荣获第十一届（2013年度）全国博物馆十大陈列展览 精品奖”、“国家AAAA级旅游景区”、“加拿大蒙特利尔室内设计金奖”（在35个获奖设计中，这是唯一以博物馆内容为主题的设计）、“省级文明单位”、“河南省爱国主义教育基地”、“河南省社会科学普及基地”、“省级卫生先进单位”等国家、省、市级荣誉20余项。2018年5月18日，平顶山博物馆与河南博物院签署战略合作框架协议，成立河南博物院平顶山分院。平顶山博物馆是观众领略深厚文化底蕴、触及悠久历史脉络、感受辉煌建设成就、享受文化发展成果的人文殿堂。在收藏、研究、宣传、推介，利用平顶山文化遗产方面发挥作用；为塑造平顶山形象、展示平顶山魅力、提升平顶山品位方面发挥独特作用。</span></a></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">特色文化活动：</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">1.“云走鹰飞—话鹰城”历史课堂系列活动；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">2.“暑期志愿者培训”活动；&nbsp;</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">3.“牡丹节”惠民演出；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">4. 博物馆日专题活动；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">5. 传统文化节”活动。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">日常开展活动</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">:</strong></span></a><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">1.博物馆基本陈列展；</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">2.博物馆临时展览日活动。</span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562578047394526.jpg\" title=\"1562578047394526.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></a></p>','2',1,'1562578075',' 平顶山市长安大道与怀仁路交叉口平安广场西侧 ',50,0,0.00,0.00),(20,5,10,'二郎山景区','轻松舒畅','AAAA','08:00-18:00','','','','/uploads/20190708/d2095e0c398d94d343b73205d9f33710.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/004df1348562c2b947e64ef43ff15900.jpg','<p><img class=\"loadingclass\" id=\"loading_jxu6rb2g\" src=\"http://xiangyan.dd371.com/static/admin/assets/js/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" title=\"正在上传...\"/><a helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">二郎山景区位于石漫滩水库南岸，国家AAAA级旅游景区、全国青少年户外活动营地。景区因“二郎担山赶太阳”而得名，由尖山、平山、鏊山、谢山、凉山、长岭山、孤山七座山峰组成，山谷曲折、林海茫茫。各类自然、人文景观景点100余处。集休闲度假、康体养生、户外拓展于一体。景区依山而建，临水而立，偎依市区，山、水、林、城浑然一体，湖光山色美不胜收。漫步于惊险刺激的水上吊桥，颤颤悠悠给人以飘飘欲仙之快感；徜徉于中国最长最美的水上古栈道，尽情感受携山踏浪之豪迈；登临中原最长、高百余米的3D玻璃悬索桥似漫步云端；加盟文化艺术表演、泼水狂欢节、龙舟竞赛、篝火晚会等娱乐项目，带给我们异样的悸动；优悠于平山、尖山之顶，欣赏自然山水那浓墨重彩的美丽画卷。近年来，二郎山景区投资5000万，对北山门广场、水上栈道、龙舟竞渡码头、游船码头、竹筏漂游码头和水上大舞台等基础设施进行提档升级，景区面貌焕然一新。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562578385763524.jpg\" alt=\"1-二郎山全景\" title=\"1-二郎山全景\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" max-width:=\"\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">二郎神担山追日浮雕：浮雕图文并茂、生动形象地介绍了二郎山的由来。说起二郎神，在我们当地广为流传着一个美丽的神话故事：相传，盘古开天地，天上十个太阳共存，烈火炎炎。后羿接连射掉了九个太阳，可九个太阳的热量全聚集在了一个太阳之上，虽然分了昼夜，仍炙热似火，万物焦枯、民不聊生。二郎神杨戬挺身而出，向玉帝请旨，要担山追日，遮蔽强光。玉帝准请，&nbsp;杨戬担起泰山脚下两座大山，日复一日紧追不舍。他担山走到现在的舞钢市境内，因倒鞋内的沙子耽误了时间，太阳远他而去。为追上太阳，二郎神杨戬心急如焚，情急之下，扁担眼挑穿，两山落地，扁担脱肩。杨戬抡起扁担对着误事的大山劈去，山头应声落下。因二郎杨戬无法再担起大山，两座山便留在了此地，并且两山相对而立，被削去山头的西山叫平山，东山为尖山。如今担山的两个扁担眼尚在,东扁担眼为二郎神洞，西扁担眼为送子观音殿。担山扁担抛在两山南侧，成了长岭山……。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">二郎神杨戬担山蔽日救天下黎民的诚意感动了天地，太阳收敛了强光，人们从此得以安居乐业。由此留下来的尖、平、孤、鏊、凉、谢、长岭七座山峰呈七星拱月之势，就是现在的二郎山。二郎神杨戬担山赶太阳功亏一篑，自感有辱使命，悲痛万分，眼泪夹带着石块漫过河滩，形成了今天的石漫滩。杨戬也被封为二郎山的山神，与这里的百姓同甘共苦，这一站就是一万八千年。&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><div><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">为感念二郎神拯救天下黎民脱离苦难的壮举，二郎山旅游开发有限公司重塑了高13.9米的二郎神杨戬汉白玉真身。</span><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">森林氧吧：景区内植被丰富，森林覆盖率达到96%以上，素有森林氧吧之美誉。这里的树木大多数都是麻栎树，据专家测定，这里的负氧离子含量是城市居民聚集区的2000——6000倍。在此漫步能让您肺腑清新，轻松舒畅。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562578385111316.jpg\" alt=\"3-二郎山森林氧吧\" title=\"3-二郎山森林氧吧\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" max-width:=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">玻璃悬索桥：桥的两端分别位于二郎神杨戬担山赶太阳的两个扁担眼处。总长286米，宽两米，高148米，是中原地区跨度最大、科技含量最高、效果最震撼的3D玻璃悬索桥，给出游的人们提供了更新鲜更多元的体验。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562578386679678.jpg\" alt=\"4-二郎山玻璃悬索桥\" title=\"4-二郎山玻璃悬索桥\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" max-width:=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">观景台：风韵古朴的观景台是亭台和廊房的巧妙结合，极具古建筑风格，是一处美丽、独特的古建筑景观。这里是观赏风景的最佳位置。在观景台上举目远望，半湾湖水，一架青山，湖光山色，山水相连。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562578386170126.jpg\" alt=\"5-二郎山观景台\" title=\"5-二郎山观景台\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" max-width:=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">玉皇金殿：二郎山文化底蕴丰厚，道教文化源远流长。玉皇金殿始建于东汉，是人们为感谢拯救万民的玉皇大帝和二郎神而建。1941年被日军炸毁，二郎山景区于2000年重新修建了庄严肃穆、雄伟壮观的玉皇金殿。香火鼎盛一方，盛世越千年。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 19px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562578386643758.jpg\" alt=\"6-二郎山玉皇金殿\" title=\"6-二郎山玉皇金殿\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" max-width:=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\">竹筏漂游：二郎山山水秀丽，风景如画，为让游客体验在青山绿水间竹筏漂游的无穷乐趣和悠然自在的美妙感受，景区特聘江南水乡的能工巧匠按照传统制作工艺，精心制作了十分坚固的竹筏。古朴原始的竹筏漂游，是一道亮丽的风景线。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562578387763903.jpg\" alt=\"7-二郎山竹筏漂游\" title=\"7-二郎山竹筏漂游\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" max-width:=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">神仙渡吊桥：桥身主体由槽钢、方钢、钢绳、方木构成，桥座为钢筋混凝土结构，桥基深入水下6米。吊桥横跨水面全长近239米，宽2.5米，距水面高6米。漫步于惊险刺激的吊桥，颤颤悠悠，飘飘欲仙。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562578387706894.jpg\" alt=\"8-二郎山神仙渡吊桥\" title=\"8-二郎山神仙渡吊桥\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562578676311789.jpg\" title=\"1562578676311789.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</p></div>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">常年举办的特色活动</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">槐花节、亲水狂欢节</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要游览线路</strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">登山线路：青少年国防教育基地—二郎神广场—游客服务中心—植物造型园—二郎神洞—中原第一桥（自费）—观景台—玉皇金殿—森林氧吧—龙壁瀑布—盆景园。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">亲水线路：走神仙渡吊桥—竹筏漂游—3D电影（自费）—水上古栈道—水上大舞台/文化艺术表演—龙舟竞赛—爱情岛—沙滩浴场—乘船游览石漫滩水库（自费）或游忘忧谷—送子观音殿。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><br/></p>','3,4',1,'1562578708','平顶山市舞钢市尹集镇石漫滩水库南岸 ',50,0,0.00,0.00),(21,5,10,'灯台架','轻松舒畅','AAAA','全年，24小时营业','','','','/uploads/20190708/7f55cbbe355067fc110a2a1aa5ef2059.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/34cf0ef6a98e16b34389cc7dc072a8d1.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">灯台架景区因主峰酷似古代灯台而得名，是国家AAAA级旅游景区，面积56平方公里，主峰海拔808米，有111个景点，35处古迹，精品景观以天池飞瀑、绝壁回廊、悬崖栈道、清潭大峡谷、猴府洞天等为代表。景区以秀丽的山水为主体，以旖旎的自然风光为特色，以脍炙人口的传奇故事和革命老区斗争史为内涵，素有森林氧吧、植物王国、古海洋遗迹地质博物馆之誉。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">灯台架地质地貌奇特，山体为砾岩、石英砂岩、页岩、白云岩等丰富多样的岩类。陈列着龟裂、冰晶、金钱斑等数十种古气候遗迹化石和原始海底及百余处岩洞石棚。这奇特的地质地貌，是经过12.8亿年以来，漫长历史演变和历次造山构造运动变迁，以及新生代以来风化剥蚀作用展现出来的深藏地下的地球历史，极具考古、科研和观赏价值。灯台架景区自去年以来投资3000万，新建了玻璃吊桥、观光电梯、双人玻璃水滑道、3A星级公厕等工程，扩建了停车场广场、亲水游步道等项目，并按照国家5A级标准重新制作安装了标识牌、景区吸引力、影响力进一步增强。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579237159381.jpg\" alt=\"2-灯台架天池瀑布2\" title=\"2-灯台架天池瀑布2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">天池：天池是天然形成的水池。天池潭深13米，三面悬崖，壁高30余米，状若巨瓮，瀑布飞珠溅玉般从天而降，在池底汇成清澈寒潭，温度在15度左右，冬暖夏凉。天池形成于距今200万年的冰川时期，是典型的冰斗。相传玉皇大帝的四公主和众姐妹因贪恋凡间，偷偷下界游玩不愿离开，随手拔下金簪划出来一道瀑布，在这里玩水嬉戏。1995年仲夏，杨成武将军亲笔题字“天池”。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579237677978.jpg\" alt=\"3-灯台架植物王国\" title=\"3-灯台架植物王国\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">植物王国：灯台架景区的植物珍稀丰富，植物种类达600多种，属于国家保护的珍稀植物有银杏、金钱松、水杉、翠柏、胡桃、青檀、长叶云杉、天目木兰、厚朴等30余种。景区内林木覆盖率达96％。松杉苍翠，绿浪起伏；红枫、白桦、青檀、黄精等千姿百态、媲美争辉。密林之中，芳草萋萋，山花摇曳，绿凉袭人。丰富的物种，良好的植被，使这里变成了名副其实的“森林氧吧”、“植物王国”。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579238952999.jpg\" alt=\"4-灯台架天井\" title=\"4-灯台架天井\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">天井：天井四面峭壁、犬牙交错，瀑布高达100余米，从井口水帘洞落下，在石壁中部凿成一池接着飞泻而下的瀑布，再缓慢送下井底，形成了自然奇观。这也是地壳运动变化的杰作。传说玉皇大帝得知女儿们经常下界游玩，非常震怒，便前去质问。四女儿说这里的水甘甜可以酿酒，玉皇大帝便派天神取水酿酒，果然酒水甘美，就命天神在此开凿一口井，因此叫天井。并派风雨雷电四位天神镇守于此，保佑这里风调雨顺，即使到了干旱的季节这里也不会断流。灯台架景区有无数迷人的山泉、溪流、瀑布与深潭，“飞瀑挂绝壁，幽泉石上流”是对景区水形态的真实写照。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579239950689.jpg\" alt=\"5-灯台架悬崖栈道1\" title=\"5-灯台架悬崖栈道1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">悬崖栈道：这是一条于悬崖峭壁之上，深沟险壑之间，架起的一条全长2000多米，宽3米—5米的通向灯台架主峰的盘山悬崖栈道。栈道依附绝壁、下临深渊、气势恢宏。蜿蜒曲折的栈道把交错纵横的深谷和千姿百态的峰林融会贯通，形成了曲折迂回、雄奇伟岸的壮美画卷。漫步在栈道之上，尤如穿云破雾，“高崖万仞通天去，闲云几片日边裁”的豪迈之气油然而生。在这里，远望，可领略高山整体气势之壮美，近观，可品察山石树木形色质纹之奇秀。更突出了灯台架景区“古海洋遗迹博物馆”和“峡谷奇观”特色，被誉为中原最惊险刺激的原生态悬崖栈道。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579241999448.jpg\" alt=\"6-灯台架仙人棚\" title=\"6-灯台架仙人棚\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">仙人棚：燃灯道人是道教鼻祖原始天尊的弟子，日后加入了西方教，成为燃灯佛。他曾在灯台架清修，这座石棚据说是因燃灯道人经常在此午休而得名。该石棚可供游人在此歇息、乘凉、避雨。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579241218408.jpg\" alt=\"7-灯台架三叠瀑\" title=\"7-灯台架三叠瀑\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">三叠瀑：灯台架有自然人文景观136处，无不体现深谷峡峪的灵气神韵。特别是景区独有的峡谷地貌“青檀大峡谷”，使我们可以欣赏大自然的五彩缤纷，变幻万千。三叠瀑完美呈现了“一瀑三叠、清泉飞泻”的壮美景观。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579381424354.jpg\" title=\"1562579381424354.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">常年举办的特色活动</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">杜鹃花节</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要游览线路</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">望灯桥—八卦图喷泉—百瀑仙溪—迎仙桥—天池—谦门—天梯—天门—天官亭—天神棚—玻璃吊桥（自费）—望灯石/情侣岩—青檀大峡谷—猴府洞天—观景台—原始海底或若克里滑道（自费）—怡心亭—绝壁回廊—悬崖栈道—悬崖谷—天井—高山水滑道下行（自费）。</span></p>','3,4',1,'1562579404','河南省平顶山市舞钢市杨庄乡长岭头村 ',50,0,0.00,0.00),(22,5,0,'香山普门禅寺','舒适','AAAA','夏季7:00——17:30 冬季7:00——16:30','','','','/uploads/20190708/2d1af5dd784167617083c9050ed3e17b.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/3334be5dcbc1bbb2709b4076c4dfac6a.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">香山普门禅寺又称香山寺，坐落于平顶山市新城区北5公里的大香山上，占地约6万平方米，满山苍翠，景色怡人，为国家4Ａ级景区，国家重点文物保护单位。是观音菩萨修行证果之地，被称为真香山，大香山、观音祖庭。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579545543455.jpg\" alt=\"香山景区2\" title=\"香山景区2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">据香山寺碑刻记载，香山寺始建于东汉光和四年（公元181年），距今有一千八百多年的历史文化传承，是现在已知的中国早期佛寺之一，在中国佛教史和观音文化史上具有重要的不可替代的地位，其宗教根文化特征非常突出。在东汉、两晋、南北朝、唐、宋等朝代，都是皇家寺院，在唐代更是被佛教界公认是“观音菩萨证道之地”和“菩萨肉身舍利存放之地”。近代两岸四地高僧大德给予香山普门禅寺以“观音祖庭”和“大香山”等称呼。</span></a></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579545484038.jpg\" alt=\"香山景区6\" title=\"香山景区6\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">香山普门禅寺有三大镇寺之宝， 1.宋熙宁元年（公元1068年）神宗皇帝敕建重修的观音大士塔；2.宋代用千年香樟木雕刻的千手千眼观世音菩萨圣像；3.宋元符三年（公元1100年）由汝州知州蒋之奇润色，翰林院大学士蔡京书丹的《香山大悲菩萨传》碑，此碑记述了菩萨修行证道的过程。</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579546661752.jpg\" alt=\"香山景区10\" title=\"香山景区10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://xiangyan.dd371.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579546256408.jpg\" alt=\"香山景区11\" title=\"香山景区11\" style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">2008年香山普门禅寺开始恢复重建，先后建成了南北牌坊、南北山门、天王殿、大慈悲殿、地藏殿、妙吉祥殿、伽蓝殿、祖师殿、斋堂、居士院、上客堂、方丈室、大势至殿、香山讲堂、念佛堂、无碍居、南北管理房、僧寮等，寺院内部红石铺地，清净庄严。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562579690878877.jpg\" title=\"1562579690878877.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span></p>','','','','3,4',1,'1562579714','平顶山市新城区香山大道北5公里 ',50,0,0.00,0.00);
INSERT INTO `ddsc_spot` VALUES (23,5,9,'画眉谷景区','轻松舒畅','AAAA','8:00-18:00（遇季节不同稍有调整）','','','','/uploads/20190708/48538eeb3de66f25f9d191621d0f835e.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/961fc15cf4031c9309b68134bc4b61cb.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">画眉谷景区，植被茂密，景色优美，自然风光迷人；景区内潭瀑成串，象连缀起来的珍珠熠熠生辉。有崇山峻岭环伺，有悬崖深谷耸峙，小溪清澈，飞瀑直倾，如轻柔的耳语倾诉，又似滔滔不绝激昂的表白：高山流水的音韵铿锵。曲径通幽，有湖光山色映照，共天光云影徘徊；鸟语花香，看龙飞凤舞祥瑞，令驻足留连叹观！好一派田园风光，山水画廊！画眉鸟、画眉谷，天地大美中的灵秀化身！</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562580168554974.jpg\" alt=\"画眉谷2\" title=\"画眉谷2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562580169343462.jpg\" alt=\"画眉谷3\" title=\"画眉谷3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">画眉谷景区位于平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇四道河村，总面积99平方公里。景区始建于 2002 年 11 月，2004 年 4 月正式接待游客，2007年 12 月被批准为国家AAA级旅游景区，2011年晋升为国家AAAA级旅游景区，集景区自然观光、休闲度假、拓展、会展培训，漂流避暑、娱乐食宿为一体，很好地满足了游客食宿行、游购娱的基本需求。在市场上有着良好服务口碑及品牌美誉度，是一张平顶山旅游的亮丽名片，吸引着八方游客纷至沓来！</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562580169339426.jpg\" alt=\"画眉谷10\" title=\"画眉谷10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562580170281929.jpg\" alt=\"画眉谷12\" title=\"画眉谷12\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562580225643739.jpg\" title=\"1562580225643739.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要景点详细介绍：</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">1、游山玩水，娱乐休闲区：设有诸多参与互动性项目，在景区入口到杜鹃湖之间，以嬉水、游乐为主；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">2、瀑布红石峡区：以小溪水、瀑布、高峡平湖、环球飞车表演观赏为主；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">3、原始森林区：以六叠瀑布、玻璃桥、悬崖栈道、观景台，及原始森林杜鹃花海的流星观赏为主。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">常年举办的特色活动：</strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">歌舞音乐狂欢节、篝火烟花晚会周周举办。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要游览线路：</strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">1、亲水步道线路：沿溪流、湖、潭，溯源而上，止六叠瀑布、玻璃桥栈道、观景台，顺滑道而下；</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">2、在景区停车场，乘坐观光车至红石峡区域，没红石瀑布往上走，到六叠瀑布、观光台，然后坐滑道下行，走杜鹃湖乘快艇下山。</span></p>','3,4,7',1,'1562580266','平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇四道河村',50,0,0.00,0.00),(24,5,11,'三苏园景区','舒适','AAAA','夏季：8：00-17：00；冬季：8：00-16：00','','','','/uploads/20190708/bbbc76aabdf4d0d1deff26737cd52d4d.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/774d0add47060b49696004f9a6e543ee.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">公元1101年8月，得赦北还的苏轼因旅途劳顿病重而逝。一代文豪就此陨落，按照苏轼生前遗愿，其子苏过扶着父亲的灵柩来到河南郏县安葬。这片饱经沧桑的大地，接纳了命运多舛的游子。后来这又成为苏辙的归宿和苏洵的衣冠冢所在，鼎盛文风从三苏园吹送而出，这就是地处郏县西北处的三苏园景区。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">三苏园景区位于郏县城西北23公里处的“小峨眉”山下，早在1963年就被河南省人民政府定为省第一批重点文物保护单位，2006年6月晋升为全国重点文物保护单位，10月被确定为国家AAA级旅游景区，11月被评为“中国县域旅游品牌百强景区”。2012年11月晋升为国家AAAA级旅游景区。三苏园文物景区主要由东坡湖、广庆寺、三苏祠、三苏纪念馆、东坡碑林、东坡中年布衣塑像、金娃迎宾道、苏仲南夫妇墓、梁氏墓和三苏陵园等景点组成。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581056943625.jpg\" alt=\"三苏园景区东门\" title=\"三苏园景区东门\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">东坡湖位于广庆寺前甬道东侧，南北长约300米，东西宽50—300米不等，东坡湖包括湖面、护坡、湖心岛以及相关附属设施等，总占地200余亩。东坡湖是2002年为了纪念东坡先生葬郏县900周年暨中国十四届苏轼学术研究会而建的人造景观。东坡湖湖面面积66亩，与苏东坡66岁阳寿相对应。湖内小岛总面积约1102平方米，小岛到堤岸的距离为6.25米，这与东坡先生葬郏的时间1102年6月25日相吻合，以示纪念。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581056763972.jpg\" alt=\"东坡湖\" title=\"东坡湖\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">广庆寺位于东坡湖西北方向，始建于宋仁宗年间，后经元至顺年间改造而成，是一座我国传统的四合院寺院建筑。主要由南天门、天王殿、大雄宝殿、东西厢房和钟、鼓楼组成。广庆寺其建筑结构与众不同，它汇集了元、明、清三个朝代的建筑特点，最明显的特征就是一进三院，寺祠合一，这在全国是极为少见的。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581056615852.jpg\" alt=\"广庆寺\" title=\"广庆寺\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">三苏祠堂是元至正年间（公元1350年）郏县尹杨允拜祭苏坟时所首创。三苏祠堂内的三苏塑像为元代所塑，栩栩如生，距今已有600多年的历史，是目前全国唯一保存最早、最完整的三苏泥彩塑像，具有极高的文物研究价值。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581057695009.jpg\" alt=\"三苏祠\" title=\"三苏祠\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">东坡碑林是为了纪念东坡先生病逝九百周年，弘扬中华民族优秀传统文化，在郏县县委、县政府的大力支持下，依靠社会捐资兴建的，东坡碑林于1997年下半年着手筹划，经约稿、成书、雕刻、建廊、镶嵌等项工作，于2000年底一期工程竣工。东坡碑林是继湖北黄冈之后，在东坡纪念地兴建的一座由当代著名书法家书写，以苏东坡著名诗、词、文为主要内容的大型碑林。整个碑林由大江东去碑园、东坡诗词碑园、礼赞碑园组成。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581057292450.jpg\" alt=\"三苏坟\" title=\"三苏坟\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">苏仲南夫妇墓位于三苏陵园东南方向，1969年生产队在浇灌农田时发现了被水冲开的苏仲南夫妇墓穴，发掘出来的墓志铭上写着“……宣和五年十月晦日，合葬于汝州郏城上瑞里先茔之东南巽隅……”（苏仲南系苏辙之次子），后经苏学界专家考证，确定了三苏葬郏的事实。苏仲南夫妇墓志铭现存放在河南省博物院。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">三苏陵园位于广庆寺北300米处，坐北朝南，总面积14800平方米。1963年6月，被河南省人民政府公布为第一批重点文物保护单位。陵园神道上古柏相应，石柱、石马、石羊、石虎、石人相对排列，仪仗严整。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">陵园内的红石牌坊，为清代郏县学者王尚絅所立，后至清道光甲申年知县李虎臣又将石坊重修一新，坊楣上写着四个行书大字“青山玉瘗”为王尚絅所题。两边石柱上所刻的对联：“是处青山可埋骨，佗年夜雨独伤神。”是苏轼在“乌台诗案”中被关押在御史台监狱写给弟弟苏辙的绝命诗《狱中遗子由》。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">朱德总司令曾写过一首诗：一家三父子，都是大文豪，诗赋传千古，峨眉共比高。然而这只是对三苏父子在文学成就上的肯定，他们在思想史、史学史、艺术史上同样有着巨大的贡献，尤其是苏东坡。他是我国历史上难得一见的旷世奇才，正如林语堂先生所言：像苏东坡这样的人物是人世间不可无一，难能有二的。苏东坡这个让文坛永远光荣的大才子，他神奇的文笔、渊博的学识、睿智的思想、高尚的人格、丰富的人生经历，多方面的巨大成就，还有他那份永远不变的诙谐，一直为后人所景仰。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">苏东坡祖籍河北栾城，出生在四川眉山。他一生坎坷，曾多次在地方为官，足记踏遍全国各地，而这位旷世奇才最终选择了河南作为他永久的休憩之所，就是在河南郏县一个叫三苏园的地方。三苏园景区位于河南郏县小峨眉山下，这里因安葬着宋代大文学家苏轼、苏辙两兄弟的遗骨及其父苏洵的衣冠而闻名，为历代名流雅士、文人墨客所景仰，是凭吊千古文豪的圣地，全国重点文物保护单位，国家4A级旅游景区。总占地面积680余亩，由东坡湖、广庆寺、三苏祠、东坡碑林、东坡中年布衣像、苏仲南夫妇墓及梁氏墓、三苏陵园和三苏纪念馆组成。这里有奇声“金蛙迎宾”，奇树“望乡古柏”，奇景“苏坟夜雨”。在这里你可以感受“大江东去”的豪迈，“千里共婵娟”的深情。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581230847307.jpg\" title=\"1562581230847307.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></span></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">常年举办的特色活动：</strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">清明公祭三苏文化活动；中国三苏诗会暨书法笔会；三苏园新春灯会;赏花节</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要游览线路：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">景区入口-东坡廉政佳句-三苏纪念馆-东坡中年布衣像-三苏坟-金蛙迎宾到-东坡碑林-三苏祠-广庆寺-东坡湖-东坡艺苑</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">线路指南：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">1、自驾车路线：<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">郏县洛界公路—薛店镇三苏园牌坊向北—三苏园。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">2、乘车路线：<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">郏县西客站乘坐通往三苏园的公交专线可直达景区</p>','3,4',1,'1562581261','平顶山市郏县茨芭镇苏坟村',50,0,0.00,0.00),(25,5,9,'尧山大峡谷漂流','轻松舒畅','AAAA','','','','','/uploads/20190708/0348d3be2ef80149ad455a7e51b29456.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/d88612a7631151c39198ab4b2bd30de0.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">一、尧山大峡谷漂流景区</span></p></a>2015被国家旅游局评为AAAA级景区，尧山大峡谷漂流上码头在尧山镇通往尧山（原石人山风景区）附近，下码头服务区设在尧山镇，上、下行均可方便到达。漂流全程长9公里，落差150米，河道时宽时窄，最宽处达85米，最窄处只有5米，既有急流险滩，又有平湖深潭，是漂流的理想河段。</span></p></a></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><img src=\"http://xiangyan.dd371.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581410172270.jpg\" alt=\"尧山大峡谷漂流1\" title=\"尧山大峡谷漂流1\" style=\"white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">鲁山县尧山镇地处311国道，东距平顶山市100公里，距鲁山县城60公里，距郑州、洛阳、漯河、许昌均在200公里以内，距郑尧高速仅9公里，也是通往尧山景区（原石人山风景区）的必经之路，位置优越、交通便利。上下码头均配套星级标准的卫生间，干净宽放的更衣室和洗浴室。上下码头还为游客准备了清洁明亮的快餐厅。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山大峡谷漂流成为平顶山旅游的一个新亮点，为尧山周围的景点配线提供了一个很好的选择，使游客在鲁山旅游能真正享受到“游山玩水”的乐趣。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581410322911.jpg\" alt=\"尧山大峡谷漂流2\" title=\"尧山大峡谷漂流2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">二、尧山天河漂流<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山天河漂流原名通天河漂流，位于鲁山县尧山镇大庄村，上码头位于尧山旅游区六羊山景区大门前，下码头紧邻郑尧高速出口。河道全长10公里，上下落差达238米，源流时间长达二个半小时。河道经精心设计，自然原始，浑然天成。水质清澈，达到国家饮用矿泉水标准。集瀑布、深潭、奇石、暗河、丛林、珍稀植物于一体的景观式漂流。是中原地区最具特色，配套最完善，交通最使捷，水质最清澈，河道最刺微的景观式漂流，并将以其独特的魅力成为漂流爱好者的新宠；其中漂流河道长约800米的地下暗河，让人在释压快感的同时，感受人在水上漂，如在画中游的惬意美景。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581411363884.jpg\" alt=\"尧山大峡谷漂流5\" title=\"尧山大峡谷漂流5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">三、尧山第一漂<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山第一漂位于国家5A级景区一一尧山之隅，峡谷上游，依山而建，因水而生，风景秀丽，水质纯净，是集山水观光、互动体验、休闲娱乐为一体的大型综合性旅游项目。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山第一漂以新的面貌，完善的设施，科学的布局，山泉激荡，长度适宜，着重考虚了游客体验，不但惊险刺激，而且安全无优，是盛夏亲水娱乐、休闲避署的绝佳场所。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山第一漂全长约八公里，落差209米，最宽处50米，最窄仅2米，信马由缰，收放自如，河道曲折蜿蜓，时而平湖深潭，时而激流滩浅，奇峰异石相伴，随处飞瀑流泉，在激情与惊呼中体验惊喜连连，不但可以随时掬一捧山泉水洗洗脸，还可以“惹是生非”打个水仗，远离城市纷扰，自由留住心田，仿佛回到了天真的童年。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">郑尧高速直达，距离高速口咫尺之遥，自驾，随团两相宜，激情就在身边，快乐如此简单。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581411867213.jpg\" alt=\"尧山大峡谷漂流3\" title=\"尧山大峡谷漂流3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">四、尧山梦幻漂流<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">山上青天山下溪，白云流水两相宜”，尧山梦幻漂流，位于鲁山县尧山镇下河村，漂流河段全长8公里，落差达108米。是由尧山大峡谷漂流集团耗资千万精心打造的又一漂流力作。漂流河道完美地保留了其原始风貌，让人在漂流之时就有与原生态世界浑然一体之感。两岸山色秀丽，沿途悬崖耸峙，急流险滩一处接一处，深潭、瀑布一个挨一个，可谓是九曲十八弯三十六道拐。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581412257565.jpg\" alt=\"尧山大峡谷漂流4\" title=\"尧山大峡谷漂流4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">其中一公里的暗河漂流，为国内少有的声光电暗河漂流，经设计师精心设计，五光十色，灯光闪烁，如进入梦幻世界，整个漂流风景如梦如画。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581557419116.jpg\" title=\"1562581557419116.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>','','','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">经营范围：水上漂流服务、旅游开发、游览景区管理服务、滑雪等</span></p></a></p>','3,7',1,'1562581613',' 鲁山县尧山镇下坪村 ',50,1,0.00,0.00),(26,5,9,'中国墨子文化旅游区','轻松舒畅','AAAA','8：00——20：30','','','','/uploads/20190708/374c2fcfa5ec349cf92991fcdcd16983.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/2e299d9ef5b065c0ea2c4e5c3276743e.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">墨子（约公元前480年一前389年），名翟。河南鲁山人，是我国战国时期著名的思想家、教育家、社会活动家、科学家、军事家，墨家学派的创始人。他主张“兼相爱，交相利”、“强不执弱，富不侮贫”。毛主席曾给予墨子很高的评价，认为：“墨子是个劳动者，他是比孔子更高明的圣人。”因为与儒家截然不同的是“百姓出生的墨子及其所创立的墨家，代表并反映了劳动者的利益和要求”。在鲁山县尧山镇墨子故里地至今仍有许多关于墨子的遗迹，鲁山县于2013年1月被授予“中国墨子文化之乡”称号。在众多的文献记载、考古文物、文化遗迹，以及有口皆碑的民间传说中，墨子文化成为中国文化巨柱，是中华民族悠久文化的精髓，因而墨子文化成为地域历史文化资源中的瑰宝。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581772696389.jpg\" alt=\"墨子文化旅游区1\" title=\"墨子文化旅游区1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">大家都知道鲁山古称鲁阳，有了山东的东鲁之后，也称西鲁。鲁山是古代平民圣人墨子的故里，为了纪念古圣先贤，并弘扬其博大精深的“兼爱、非攻”思想文化，于2016年投巨资在尧山脚下滍水河畔创建了中国墨子文化旅游区（俗称墨子古街）。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581773193254.jpg\" alt=\"墨子文化旅游区4\" title=\"墨子文化旅游区4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">每天的上午九点至九点三十分在这里举行隆重、盛大、仪仗威严的墨子开门迎宾仪式。届时墨子身着皂衣，手执长剑，仪态威武、正气凛然，带领众学子、钜子，英姿飒爽，在演武场上摆开仪仗：宣讲“兼爱、非攻”的政治主张，和“入守则固，出诛则强”的治国强军理念及“赴火蹈刀、死不旋踵”视死如归的为国牺牲精神。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">墨子古街以墨子时期崇尚节俭、追求古朴、粗犷自然的建筑风格为基调，以墨子“兼爱、非攻，尚贤、节用”的十大思想主张为文化脉络，沿中华名吃一条街，特色购物一条街，滍水河岸墨子客栈，小火车窄轨铁路、四合院老作坊依次展开，坐着小火车，听着老戏楼的鼓儿词，看着街头的糖人戏耍，赏着滍水河上竹筏鸣筝，渔歌晚唱的万家灯火，在墨子古街的集市盛况中找回童年的乐趣。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581773882437.jpg\" alt=\"墨子文化旅游区7\" title=\"墨子文化旅游区7\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562581920234376.jpg\" title=\"1562581920234376.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">懒人线路</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">景区正门-墨子号观光小火车（贯穿墨子古街）-爱情谷-月老广场-银河玻璃桥--神牛滑道-原路返回-景区正门（2小时）此线路能以最短的时间到达银河玻璃桥，乘坐墨子号观光小火车，省力省时，适合亲子家庭出游或体力相对较弱的老人游览。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">素人线路<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">景区正门-鲁班桥-墨子古街-迎宾瀑-爱情谷（实景马战-仙女瀑布）-月老广场-银河玻璃桥-神牛滑道-原路返回-景区正门（3-4小时） 此线路为尧山景区中环线，沿途包含主要景点，并可观看到实景马战，适合学生、成人、登山爱好者游览。</p>','3,4,7',1,'1562581955','平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇贾店村',50,0,0.00,0.00),(27,5,10,'祥龙谷景区','舒适','AAAA','08:00-18:00','','','','/uploads/20190708/f79238d8aeeab0c4764348f87ded2761.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/ad632dfc027b4311a49d6096819cac5b.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">祥龙谷属峡谷类山水景区，山峰奇特、瀑布众多、森林茂密，人文景观辉煌，奇峰、怪石、山花、红叶、飞瀑、湖面、原始森林、珍禽异兽及人文景观构成了完整的风景体系，集&quot;雄险秀奇幽&quot;于一体，是旅游观光、避暑疗养、休闲度假、科研探险的好地方。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562582092290803.jpg\" alt=\"祥龙谷景区1\" title=\"祥龙谷景区1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">祥龙谷四季风光别致。春天鸟语花香，绿映溪吟;初夏时节使人领略&quot;人间四月芳菲尽，山寺桃花始盛开&quot;的清新景象。盛夏，当平原大地上&quot;赤日炎炎似火烧&quot;时，这里只有23-26度，凉爽宜人。秋日满山红叶，层林尽染;冬季银装素裹，林海雪原。</span></p></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562582092502304.jpg\" alt=\"祥龙谷景区3\" title=\"祥龙谷景区3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">祥龙谷景区具有较好的自然条件，植被覆盖率90%以上。景区内动、植物类型丰富，有野生植物234科，809属，1685种，属于国家保护的珍稀植物33种，仅中草药就达702种之多。既有杜鹃、山鸡等飞禽，又有松鼠、野猪、果子狸、鹳、貉等走兽。品种繁多的动植物、秀丽的景色、潺潺的小溪、神奇的峭壁、凉爽的气候构成了景区良好的生态自然环境。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">祥龙谷景区不仅有天然之色，文明遗迹也不胜枚举。东汉光武帝刘秀、北宋杨家将、南宋农民起义军&quot;蛮王&quot;、明代大将左良玉、武林大侠张三丰都在此留下了他们的遗迹，也为景区增加了深厚的文化内涵。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562582093481114.jpg\" alt=\"祥龙谷图片\" title=\"祥龙谷图片\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">龙王撞：祥龙谷景区内的最高点，海拔866 米， 是舞钢市域的最高峰。传说，原本龙王撞的山峰比现在还要高出许多，奇峰突兀，直插云霄。当时东海龙王奉玉帝之命前往伏牛山余脉一带布雨，刚下凌霄宝殿就撞在了这座山峰上，山峰被齐腰撞断。龙王一惊，此地还有如此奇峰，仔细巡查，真是宝地，就留在此地兴云布雨。因故，此峰就叫做“龙王撞”。因为龙王撞曾经是距离天庭最近的山峰，在这里祈福是最灵验的，所以后人每次来这里祈福的人都要带一块石头，希望能增加龙王撞的高度。其实，龙王撞每年都以我们肉眼看不到的高度在增高。据传，凡是登上龙王撞祈福的人，只要把心愿刻在这里的石头总能心想事成。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562582093376624.jpg\" alt=\"内文27\" title=\"内文27\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 43px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">官平院：官平院原名“观天院”，因为走过这里的“头道门”东西两边的石壁都是下边窄，上边宽，进到门里，三面都是峭壁，中间有一块平地，站在这里，抬起头来，只能看见头顶的一片蓝天，所以人们称它“观天院”。<br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">相传，当年刘秀被叛贼王莽追至祥龙大峡谷，走到此地后，刘秀又累又饿，就在靠这里的一块大石头旁休息，不知不觉地睡着了，梦里祥龙指引了他寻找援军的方向。刘秀醒来时，发现身边多了一些山果。刘秀感谢祥龙的帮助，站在此地，对天长拜后，用山果填饱了肚子，按照祥龙的指引去找救援。后来，刘秀建立东汉王朝，史称汉光武帝，重新恢复了汉室江山。为了答谢天恩，他下旨在此处修建了“观天寺院”，来祭拜祥龙。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562582449721983.jpg\" title=\"1562582449721983.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">线路指南</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">平顶山长途汽车站-舞钢长途汽车站-尹集乡-马村王-祥龙大峡谷</span></p><p><br/></p>','3,4',1,'1562582468','平顶山市舞钢杨庄乡',50,0,0.00,0.00),(28,5,12,'中国岩盐博物馆','舒适','AAA','上午08:00—11:30 下午13:30—17:00 ','','','','/uploads/20190708/4ec0a93c940f309094c41ce65968c820.png',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/6c71adaa4c2e780bfa668e68464510b0.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">一、博物馆简介</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">中国岩盐博物馆位于河南省平顶山市叶县“中国岩盐之都”，总投资2000余万元，占地面积26亩，2016年8月正式破土动工，2017年12月11日建成并对外开放。该馆展览主题“文明结晶”，由《岩盐之都》、《盐的生产》、《盐与社会》、《生命之源》四部分组成。馆内陈列以大量珍贵的文物和历史照片为基础，采用声、光、电等多媒体技术，辅助以喷绘、灯箱、图片、蜡像、雕塑、场景、沙盘模型等演示手法，突出展现了中国盐业的辉煌成就和叶县岩盐的开发进程。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583293598027.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a><br/><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">二、建馆缘由</strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">河南在历史上不产盐，属于纯销区，长期依赖外省供给，直到改革开放后，国家为了全面推进基础工业建设，在叶县勘探石油时，偶然发现在叶县境内约1100米的地下，蕴藏着一个特大型优质盐矿床——“叶县盐田”。该盐田展布面积400余平方公里，储量3300亿吨，品味居全国井矿盐之首，储量居全国第二。2007年9月29日，叶县被中国矿业联合会命名为“中国岩盐之都”。为了传承古都岩盐文化，推介叶县乃至平顶山市崭新名片，进一步带动地方旅游休闲、观光服务等相关产业发展，叶县政府和中国平煤神马集团共同出资建设了中国岩盐博物馆，可以说，该馆是应运而生，它让盐业文明和古城历史在这片土地上焕发出蓬勃生机和异样光彩。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">三、展览主题</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">（一）岩盐之都</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"></strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">叶县位于中原腹地，历史悠久，文化底蕴深厚，矿产资源丰富，岩盐储量位居全国前列。中国平煤神马集团作为一家国有特大型企业集团，立足本业、着眼全局，大力发展盐化工产业，特别是在叶县盐业开发利用方面做出了突出贡献，有力推动了地方经济蓬勃发展。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583294290951.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">（二）盐的生产</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">盐的生产方法，可简括为煮海为盐、湖池晒盐、凿井取盐。不同种类的盐在不同的历史时期有其独特的生产工艺，与当时的科学技术发展相适应。海盐的提炼技术包括煮盐和晒盐。湖盐的生产工艺经历了由集工捞采法、垦畦浇晒法到机械化开采的过程。井矿盐的生产工艺也由古代凿井法演变为现代化的旋转钻井。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583294153819.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">（三）盐与社会</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">盐与社会有着极为密切的联系。一方面，在日常生活中，盐是一种不可缺少的物质。另一方面，从古到今，盐已渗透到政治、经济、文化、军事等社会各个领域，并发挥着重要的作用，推动人类社会文明的演变。比如，历代盐税制度、典型盐商建筑、特色盐风民俗，都是盐与社会关系密切的有力例证。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583294582260.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">（四）生命之源</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">盐，不仅翻腾在浩瀚的大海上，隐藏在静谧的湖池里，埋藏在深厚的岩层中，而且还从我们每天生活都会接触到的锅碗瓢盆中转变成涌动不息的生命之源。盐中所含氯、钠、钾、碘等化学元素无时无刻不在调节身体的健康状态。盐从诞生的那一刻，就伴随着人生的酸、甜、苦、辣、咸之滋味，随着文明的车轮滚滚向前，永不停息。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583295145555.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要景点详细介绍：</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">《昆阳之战》动画场景还原。新朝末年，新汉两军在中原地区进行的一场战略决战，这场大战的主战场在昆阳一线（今河南省叶县），故称为昆阳之战。昆阳之战是中国历史上著名的以少胜多的战例之一，它决定了新汉两军的命运和未来中原王朝数百年的国运，是中国历史上一次有深远影响的战略决战。昆阳之战中，身为偏将军的刘秀一战而天下闻名，昆阳之战不但是刘秀击败王莽的关键一战，同时也为刘秀日后夺取天下奠定了基础。昆阳之战是中国以少胜多的著名战役，此战聚歼了王莽赖以维持统治的军队主力，为起义军胜利进军洛阳、长安，最终推翻新莽统治创造了有利的条件。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583378249620.jpg\" title=\"1562583378249620.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><br/></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">常年举办的特色活动：</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">含盐特色产品展示，还原燊海井制盐工艺模型动态展。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要游览线路：</strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">馆外：盐疗体验池</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">馆内：《岩盐之都》→《盐的生产》→《盐与社会》→《生命之源》</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">线路指南：</strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">叶县北→234国道→叶廉路→中国平煤神马集团联合盐化公司院内</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"></a></p><p><br/></p>','2',1,'1562583419','平顶山市叶县',50,0,0.00,0.00),(29,5,9,'阿婆寨风景区','轻松舒畅','AAA','春夏季早上7:30至18:00 秋冬季早上8:00至17:30','','','','/uploads/20190708/4d270421cfd8890ad9d9e788281b15f3.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190708/44cb1d7997c96163097b5dd61d9676da.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">阿婆寨景区位于伏牛山东麓大龙山，主峰海拔878米，境内徒崖与沟壑相融，奇石与孤峰相拥，松林与瀑布相连，果树与居民相映。春看山花烂漫，夏赏日出林海，秋醉乡村风韵，冬观松涛冰挂。景区位于河南省平顶山市鲁山县、宝丰县、汝州市的三地交界处，景区规划面积110平方公里，由深圳雷音集团旗下河南雷音旅游开发有限公司和鲁山雷音实业有限公司斥资6.7亿联合开发，是集礼佛祈福、观光禅悟、养老养生、生态农业、农事体验、山地休闲、野外拓展、人文怀古等为一体的精品景区。阿婆寨历史悠久，宗教文化底蕴深厚，是如来佛道场、西游文化发源地、长城之祖楚长城、观音修行地之有求必应的祈福圣地，被誉为佛教名山、中原福地。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a><br/><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要景点详细介绍：</strong></span></p><p></p><p><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">祈福圣地——大雷音寺</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">大雷音寺始建于东汉永平十二年（即公元69年），历经朝代更迭，如今仍经声不绝，香火兴旺。寺院坐北朝南，占地面积约360亩，东有青龙山蜿蜒盘旋，西有白虎峰气势恢宏，寺前河水潺潺如弯弓盘回。寺中含山，山中藏寺，寺中有河，水中有寺，被媒体誉为“最隐世的千年古刹”，是信众心中的“西天灵山、祈福圣地”。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583566135926.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">五龙沟瀑布群</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">五龙沟瀑布群：五龙沟位于大龙山下，全长约3000米，此沟因住着观世音菩萨的坐骑金木水火土五条龙而得名。五龙沟瀑布的形态因季节而有变化，冬季山水轻轻下泻，妩媚秀丽。到了夏秋，山水飞流而下，那撼天动地的磅礴气势，简直令人惊心动魄。有时瀑布激起的雪沫烟雾，高达百米，漫天浮游，时而出现五彩缤纷的彩虹，竟使其周围处于纷飞的细雨之中，宛如仙境。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583566766352.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">洞天福地——观音洞</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">观音洞位于阿婆寨明镜台下，洞口约高3米，宽约2米，洞深300米左右，与黄龙洞相通。因观世音菩萨在此洞修行，故得名观音洞。观音洞景点是阿婆寨景区重要景点之一，洞中藏洞、幽古生辉、冬暖夏凉、百虫不扰。观音洞是历代百姓求财祈福之圣地，被誉为“洞天福地”（因观音洞是宗教信仰圣地所以洞内暂时不对外开放）。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">明镜台</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">明镜台位于阿婆寨山怀，五龙沟之上。因观音菩萨在此修行时，经常在台上对镜梳妆打扮而得名。禅诗曰“菩提本无树，明镜亦非台，本来无一物，何处染尘埃”。明镜台的石面上，现在有佛缘的人还可以看到观音菩萨梳妆时梳子、铜镜和金簪放置的印迹。明镜台是美女梳妆的宝地，在此梳妆打扮能得到观音菩萨的保佑，青春永驻，美貌如花。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583567515018.jpg\" alt=\"8\" title=\"8\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">十里悬空栈道</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">阿婆寨栈道，全长5109米，是中原最长的悬崖栈道，是一件融入大自然的艺术作品，鬼斧神工让人叹为观止。阿婆寨十里悬空栈道，把阿婆寨的奇峰、瀑布、山泉、怪石、洞穴、古藤、珍木、野花、绝壁、峡谷等旖旎风光连成一体，形成一线，走在悬崖栈道，如临仙山蓬莱。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583567630720.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">森林氧吧</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">阿婆寨景区斛叶林森林氧吧，总面积300万平方米，是中原最大的斛叶林森林氧吧。这里是斛叶的世界，斛叶的海洋，空气中饱含着斛叶的清香。经专家采用DL-3F型树林大气离子测量仪测量，氧吧内每平方厘米中含58000-62000个对人体健康有益处的负氧离子。斛叶林森林氧吧是阿婆寨景区植被最美的自然风光和最佳的生态环境。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583569297856.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">高山花海</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">“晓迎秋露一枝新，不占园中最上春，桃李无言又何在，向风偏笑艳阳人”，此处海拔800米以上，紫薇花林中，芳草鲜美，各种野花与紫薇花竞相开放，相映生辉，漫步其间，诗情画意，胜过“桃花源”。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583569165400.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">楚长城遗址</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">鲁山阿婆寨楚长城是楚国最北边境的长城，距今2600多年的历史，修筑在悬崖峭壁上，蜿蜒在山岭之间，全长约20千米，是最早的长城，誉为“长城之祖”，是历史的见证，是世界文化遗产。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583569153221.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">阿婆寨滑道</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">阿婆寨滑道位于景区将军山下，依山势而建，与凤栖湖紧密相连，惊险刺激，安全舒适，不管男女老少皆可尽兴体验，让你在惊险刺激的滑行同时又能欣赏阿婆寨的俊秀之美。阿婆寨滑道因其自身独有的特点被众多游客赞誉为“中原第一滑”和“中国第一挂壁滑道”。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583570229954.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">玻璃天桥</strong><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">阿婆寨景区玻璃天桥，长260米，宽2米，高317米。天桥把相峙而立的凤凰头和西凤凰台紧紧连接在一起，一桥架东西，天堑变坦途。玻璃天桥就如架于天际的彩虹，盘踞长峡的蛟龙，置身万里云海，脚踏千仞空谷，头顶参天云浪，顿生“极目楚天舒”之感。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583570496829.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583748950819.jpg\" title=\"1562583748950819.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要游览线路：</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><img src=\"http://xiangyan.dd371.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190708/1562583571186112.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">线路指南：</strong><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">1、郑尧高速在下汤镇转二广高速向洛阳方向瓦屋站下，后转242省道鲁山县城方向，向东5公里烟东岭处有路标，向北（即向左）3公里左右即到。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">2、郑尧高速公路在鲁山站下高速，沿鲁山至瓦屋镇的省道242线公路行驶30公里左右，烟东岭处有指示牌，向北（即向右）3公里左右即到。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">3、洛阳、南阳方向沿二广高速瓦屋站下，后转242省道鲁山县城方向，向东5公里烟东岭处有路标，向北（即向左）3公里左右即到。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">4、从平顶山新城区经宝丰县沿S234，即平顶山至石龙区快速通道向西至石龙区207国道，沿207国道至仓头乡向西，经堂上水库、三间房村、岳村、西陈庄村、耐庄村即到<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">。</span></span></p>','3,4,7',1,'1562583798','平顶山市鲁山县瓦屋镇耐庄村雷音寺组',50,1,0.00,0.00),(30,5,9,'诗景龙潭峡','轻松舒畅','AAA','08:00-18:00','1000','5000','3000','/uploads/20190709/9e3211c6950fa56953b46e3fc6962911.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190718/98f61cf7de8b9193675bde0e264b1bd4.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">鲁山县诗景龙潭峡景区位于伏牛山腹地的河南省鲁山县尧山镇上坪村，尧山的南麓；是国家AAA级旅游景区、河南省级森林公园。景区距鲁山县城66公里，国道311、207贯穿景区，位置优越，交通便利，诗景龙潭峡景区总面积30平方公里，全长5公里，自然落差1200米，景区内已命名景点百余处，尤以一林、二溪、三峰、四洞、五奇、六瀑、七潭、八石、九果、十树最为著名，诗景龙潭峡景区以其闻名中原的通天瀑，被誉为“伏牛水魂”。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">主要景点详细介绍：</strong></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">通天瀑：诗景龙潭峡是水的世界，这里的瀑布成群，潭潭相连，以其闻名中原的通天瀑，被誉为“伏牛水魂”。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643344257001.jpg\" alt=\"龙潭峡7\" title=\"龙潭峡7\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">杜鹃花：四五月的诗景龙潭峡，一片芳菲，花香满径。随着天气的变化，山上各色杜鹃次第进入盛开期。漫山遍野、五彩缤纷，红如血、白似雪、粉若霞，如诗如画，似梦似幻。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643345370043.jpg\" alt=\"龙潭峡4\" title=\"龙潭峡4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" max-width:=\"\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643347860694.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" max-width:=\"\"/></span></p>','112.342869','33.708464','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">常年举办的特色活动：</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">揽国菜宴&nbsp; 杜鹃花节</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\">主要游览线路：</span></strong><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">墨子故居-龙潭谷-犀牛把关-龙女潭-狐狸洞-同心石-通天峡-通天瀑-天井-飞云峰-唬啸峰-一线天</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\">线路指南：</span></strong><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">（一）郑州至诗景龙潭峡景区：在郑州嵩山南路，过南四环，上郑尧高速，在尧山出站口下车，沿尧山防方向，行驶至诗景龙潭峡景区；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">（二）洛阳、南阳、焦作、济源、三门峡至诗景龙潭峡景区：上二广高速沿南阳、襄樊方向（正南）到下汤站转郑尧高速，沿尧山方向，到尧山出站口，行驶至诗景龙潭峡景区；</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, \" microsoft=\"\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">（三）安阳、濮阳、新乡、鹤壁至诗景龙潭峡景区：京珠高速到漯河，转南洛高速，到平顶山西转郑尧高速，（沿尧山方向）在尧山出站口下车，行驶至诗景龙潭峡景区。</span><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643523687061.jpg\" title=\"1562643523687061.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</p>','3,4',1,'1562643641','河南省平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇上坪村',50,1,0.00,0.00);
INSERT INTO `ddsc_spot` VALUES (31,5,12,'叶县县衙博物馆','轻松舒畅','AAA','全年 8:30—17:30','','','','/uploads/20190709/af56e915f7450f3ad5884913235d03bc.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190709/88fbb8c3a357fea99a6b1a51009c9fc6.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">叶县县衙博物馆是国家AAA旅游景区，全国重点文物保护单位，始建于明代洪武二年（公元1369年），座落于县城中心街北侧，占地面积16848平方米是目前我国现存三座古县衙中唯一的明代县衙。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643751786185.jpg\" alt=\"县衙博物馆夜景\" title=\"县衙博物馆夜景\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">整座建筑布局共有41个单元，153间房屋组成，具有重要的历史价值、艺术价值和科学价值。叶县县衙群落布局合理，规模宏大，是我国古代县级衙署中为数不多的幸存者。其建筑形式融南北之风格，对研究我国古代建筑的风格、流派特点及变化规律等都具有重要的价值。同时也是研究我国古代县级政权机构的重要实物依据。</span></a></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643751172188.jpg\" alt=\"县衙博物馆2\" title=\"县衙博物馆2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643751387914.jpg\" alt=\"县衙博物馆5\" title=\"县衙博物馆5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">叶县县衙整体布局由中轴线和东、西侧副线上的建筑群体组成。位于中轴线上的建筑主要有大门、仪门、卷棚、大堂、宅门、二堂、三堂及所附属的东西班房、六科房和东西厢房等组成；东侧副线分别为厨院、知县宅及狱房等建筑；西侧副线依次为西群房、虚受堂、思补斋等建筑；三堂后为大仙祠和后花园；大门东侧有编钟演奏厅和文物展厅。文物库房及展厅建筑面积473平方米，分文物库房、精品文物展厅、监控室、值班室等部分，从1000多件库存文物中选出300多件精品进行展览，其中有70多件文物为全国仅存的稀世珍宝。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643752808187.jpg\" alt=\"县衙博物馆4\" title=\"县衙博物馆4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643752516290.jpg\" alt=\"县衙博物馆3\" title=\"县衙博物馆3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">叶县县衙自对外开放以来先后荣获：“国家AAA级旅游景区”、“全国重点文物保护单位”、“市级廉政教育基地”、“市级党性教育基地教学点”、“平顶山市爱国主义教育示范基地”“河南中小学专项性社会实践教育基地”、“河南省科普教育基地” 和“平顶山市科<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">普教育基地”等荣誉</span>。目前，叶县县衙共接待中外游客300余万人次，是叶县对外开放的重要窗口。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"></span><br/></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"></a></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">特色文化活动</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">1、“县官审案”演艺活动</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">2、“改革开放四十年”迎春书画摄影展</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">3、“编钟演奏”现场演出</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562643902325142.jpg\" title=\"1562643902325142.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>','2,3',1,'1562643934','平顶山市叶县东大街',50,1,0.00,0.00),(32,5,9,'好运谷景区','轻松舒畅','AAA','8：00——17：30','1000','3000','2000','/uploads/20190709/9cb0e4b39e408631ec7b38faab4a5266.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190709/411cf1d00319b30a8e83ee407e004f27.jpg','<p><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family:; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\" helvetica=\"\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family:; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\" helvetica=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\">好运谷景区两岸，郁郁丛丛，群峰峙立，竟奇斗峻；断崖重重，险不可攀；奇石如塑，似人似物；石穴洞府，幽深莫测；原始森林，遮天蔽日；野果累累，芳香诱人；奇花异卉，漫山遍野;金秋红叶、流丹似火。尤为著名的是谷中成群成串的飞瀑、龙潭及广阔的湖面、依山势高低错落、飘逸洒脱、布局巧妙、紧凑合理，成为自然山水中的奇葩。</span></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; font-family:; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\" helvetica=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><img title=\"好运谷3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; -ms-word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\" alt=\"好运谷3\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562644552495688.jpg\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; -ms-word-break: break-all; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"></a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; display: inline !important; -ms-word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\">好运谷景区地处车村——下汤深断裂带的中部，断裂破碎的花岗岩地貌嵯峨嶙峋，奇峰怪石比比皆是。十八垛雄居峰巅，如顶天立地的十八罗汉；光石脑矗立中天，似统领百万大军的常胜将军。红石崖，白松崖，羚羊楼，峰峻壁直。更有数不尽的如塑怪石，似人似物，老翁石、寿星石、金佛石、河马石、猴石、美鱼石、龙床石、蛙鼓石、盘古开天碾盘石和传说中月宫嫦娥舂米的神臼石。还有许许多多的神秘洞穴，如藏龙洞、水帘洞、豹子洞、狼洞、哑巴洞、红军洞、省心洞、和清朝开挖锰矿留下的“老银洞”。各洞有异，洞洞有奇。好运谷景区上部为十八垛原始林区，中下部为天然次生林区。植物种类多，林木遮天蔽日，奇花异卉，举目可见。春季杜鹃满山，如血似火，林翠草青，满山知了大合唱，动听悦耳。金秋时节，红叶流丹，五彩缤纷，野果山珍挂满枝头。隆冬，道道飞瀑，形成冰帘冰挂，壁潭成冰，形成天然冰场，雾淞雪凇，玲珑剔透，此时的水帘洞，更如冰中洞府，风景迷人。盛夏，谷中凉爽清新，观飞瀑抒怀，听山溪欢歌，或泳涤于碧潭，或摩嬉于鱼蟹。若龙之潜渊，若鱼之得水。山情野趣，原始自然，惬意舒心，真乃仙境之地！</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img width=\"204\" height=\"140\" title=\"好运谷2\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; width: 610px; height: 384px; -ms-word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\" alt=\"好运谷2\" src=\"http://xiangyan.dd371.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562644552785398.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">好运谷景区——戏水山庄</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">好运谷景区地灵人杰，民风纯朴，富有光荣革命传统。一九三四年，红二十五军长征经此，山民曾为红军带路至红石关（即没大岭）。一九四五年六月，河南人民抗日军挺进鲁山，创建伏牛山抗日根据地。在胡宗南九十军的疯狂进攻下，部队被迫退至好运谷一带的山林中与敌人周旋。以陈先瑞为司令员的三支队司令部曾驻扎于好运谷中部的西沟。当地农民李成明、李文海、钱振江曾把八部军的30多名伤病员藏在山谷中的石洞里，悬崖上、密林中，送药送饭，悉心照料，长达4个月到一年以上。任凭敌人严刑拷打，威逼利诱，始终没有暴露。如今，当年曾为伤病员送药送饭，通风报信的李文举、李春富、在好运谷口朴素曲雅的农家院里，每天都在为游客介绍着那段惊心动魄的革命斗争故事。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><img width=\"326\" height=\"227\" title=\"好运谷1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; width: 323px; height: 242px; -ms-word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\" alt=\"好运谷1\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562644553125889.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">好运谷景区内有许多动听的故事和优美的神话传说。这些颇具传奇色彩的故事传说，使得好运谷的景观更加有血有肉，活灵活现。徜徉于好运谷的山不间，犹如走进了一条画廊，走进了一段历史，在原始自然中受到人生的启迪。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体,SimSun; font-size: 16px;\">好运谷景区，是一曲水的乐章。观瀑游潭之余，食宿于谷口的农家院，环境幽雅，物美价廉。就近到好运湖中荡舟、游泳，兴许还真会沾上一身好运气，从此而吉祥如意，好事连连呢！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\"><img title=\"1562644654358884.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190709/1562644654358884.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; border: 0px currentColor; border-image: none; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -ms-word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</p>','112.345135','33.787974','','2,3,4,7',1,'1562644673','平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇四道河',50,1,0.00,0.00),(33,5,9,'秘洞景区','轻松舒畅','AAA','08:00-18:00','','','','/uploads/20190710/346349a6f7021ba58eb5cc39efd36ea4.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190710/247b59cbbba3240a9fb90cbd462ad0fd.jpg','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562725240977432.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;\"/></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">秘洞景区位于河南省鲁山县西南部尧山下，距鲁山县城、尧山主要景区均为45公里，距207国道1公里，与石林路、军航路相互贯通。公司成立于2009年，累计接待游客量30余万人次，2011年被评定为AAA级景区。景区总占地面积约360亩。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">该景区内的建筑群落均为二十世纪六十年代末、七十年代初动用军工历时三年半，耗资数亿元修建而成的地下军事指挥中心。主要由地面建筑和地下建筑两部分组成，共占地十余万平方米。地面建筑主要有房屋16栋、167间，依山傍水，隐蔽于红花绿树丛中。地下建筑主要有指挥洞、作战洞、通讯洞三部分组成，还有暗道、暗堡、暗哨数处。</span></a><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">秘洞是响应毛主席“备战备荒为人民”号召建设的地下“反修防修”指挥工程，秘洞是“三线” 建设时期的见证，反映了一个时期的辉煌，是智慧和汗水的结晶。秘洞是我国军事防御理念的集中体现，代表当时军事科技的最高水平，是地下防空军事工程的典范之作。现存的地上建筑17栋167间3936.63平方米，分布在河道两侧，依山而建。油机房、锅炉房、车库、伙房、营房，都是用不规则的石块砌成，做工非常精细，下部都有出水孔，有防潮的作用，顶非常坚固，虽历经40多年风雨，仍旧不漏雨。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562725241477068.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">指挥洞长300米，高6米，宽5米，可容纳大卡车出入。洞口置有八道防化门，坚如磐石，牢不可破，还有集军事化、科学化、现代化为一体的工作、生活、娱乐设施。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562725242906891.jpg\" alt=\"秘洞7\" title=\"秘洞7\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">作战洞长350米，高3米，宽2.5米，有房间110多个，是庞大的军事作战指挥场所。洞内作战所需的一切系统，配置完备 ，布局合理，可遥控指挥全国战局。可谓“运筹帷幄之中，决胜千里之外。”</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562725242193955.jpg\" alt=\"秘洞6\" title=\"秘洞6\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">在今天和平时期，秘洞具有很高的历史教育价值。虽然秘洞的军事作用已成历史，但在当时困难的政治、经济、自然条件下，特别是当年广大解放军官兵在建设中表现出来的革命加拼命精神，严守纪律和自我牺牲精神，大公无私和先人后己精神，压倒一切艰难险阻，压倒一切困难的精神，坚持革命乐观主义，排除万难争取胜利的精神，也是永远值得发扬的宝贵精神财富。 这个军事旧址正在成为冷战文化重构的新标本。那遗留下来的军事遗址，那壮观的工程，在今天，依然让我们肃穆！它是军事智慧的经典之作，它是中华民族不屈不挠的象征，折射出中华民族防御战略和军事博弈的发展脉络，也因此成为我们今天战略思维的军事文化遗产。改革开放后，经过修整，改名“秘洞景区”，为游人开放。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562725243811411.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">秘洞景区风光秀丽，环境清静幽雅，自然景色奇特壮观，世间独有，这里古木参天，瀑布常流，水声潺潺，鸟语花香，由军营改建而成的宾馆，冬暖夏凉，四季如春，而且干净、整洁、舒适、是休闲，度假、避暑、疗养的绝好去处。</span></a></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">主要游览线路</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;\">山门-猕猴长廊-展示厅-指挥洞-停机坪-桂花林-下山步道-山门</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">线路指南</strong></a><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">1、郑尧高速下汤站下，左转走207国道直达</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">2、 二广高速转郑尧高速郑州方向下汤站下，左转走207国道直达(二广高速下汤西高速口因有限宽，请绕道行驶)</span></a><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\">3、南阳地区二广高速转郑尧高速下汤站下，走207南召方向。</span></a><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: 