in-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山滑雪度假乐园位于河南省平顶山市鲁山县尧山北麓，紧临中原大佛、尧山、画眉谷、木扎岭及鲁山上、中、下汤温泉群。交通便捷，雪场紧临311国道，距郑尧高速出口18公里，距郑州190公里，是河南省内组合线路最好，交通最便捷的高山滑雪场。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&quality=80&size=b9999_10000&sec=1561130194847&di=a6d30490c9daded0ef8fcd1d0fba5b55&imgtype=0&src=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.my519.net%2Ffiles%2F2013-11%2F20131130102955170145.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562725984616082.jpg\" alt=\"尧山滑雪乐园1\" title=\"尧山滑雪乐园1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山滑雪度假乐园占地面积20万平方米，其中雪场面积3万平方米，雪具大厅3000平方米。滑雪乐园一期建设初、中级雪道各1条，雪地魔毯2条，雪道宽100米，长度近500米，最大坡度18度，最小坡度5度。雪场引进国际先进的造雪、压雪设备和全新的配套服务设施，并设有雪上飞碟娱乐区，儿童专业的滑雪乐园地，真正做到了赏雪、玩雪、娱雪的全方位功能。</span></p><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562725985133527.jpg\" alt=\"尧山滑雪乐园2\" title=\"尧山滑雪乐园2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山滑雪度假乐园与鲁山温泉疗养、中原大佛祈福、尧山赏雪形成绝佳的冬季旅游热线，在近30公里的范围内，实现了生态休闲度假、天然健康温泉与时尚滑雪的完美融合，必将成为中原冬季旅游的最佳目的地！</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562725986193223.jpg\" alt=\"尧山滑雪乐园3\" title=\"尧山滑雪乐园3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山滑雪乐园将以一流的设施、优质的服务，让您感受专业级的滑雪体验和贵宾礼遇，让您畅享冬季滑雪旅游的激情体验！</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山滑雪乐园有一条150米长的初级道，一条480米长的中级道，一条190米长的雪圈道。</span></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"></a></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">为了让较高水平的滑雪者更好的体验滑雪的激情，尧山滑雪乐园还特意在中级道南侧修建了一条长度为500米的中高级道。<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">初级道平均宽度50米，坡度3-5度，配备一条魔毯；</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">中级道平均宽度75米，坡度13度，配备2条摩毯；</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">中高级道平均宽度25米，坡度16度，和中级道共用摩毯。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">雪圈道平均宽度8米，坡度约9度，和中级道共用摩毯。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山滑雪乐园3摩毽总长度550米，是河南滑雪场中摩毯数量最多，长度最长的滑雪场。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">尧山滑雪乐园位于河南省平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇境内。从郑尧高速终点沿311国道向尧山镇、栾川方面前行20公里即抵雪场大门，下高速后到滑雪场的路况良好，指示设施完善，没有盘山公路，是河南省交通最便利的高山滑雪场<span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190710/1562726156893018.jpg\" title=\"1562726156893018.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></span></p>','3,4',1,'1562726178','河南省平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇',50,1,0.00,0.00),(36,5,13,'湛河源莲花湿地景区','轻松舒畅','AAA','8：00-18：00','','','','/uploads/20190712/ec07a0998079700287bfba8364d930e7.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190712/63f69835baf8efb23423b5bfd7493656.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">湛河源莲花湿地景区位于宝丰县城东南3公里与平顶山新城区交汇处，占地面积约1.33平方公里，交通便利，地理位置优越。宝丰县地处中原，西部青山推涌，绵延至东南方向形成文笔山岭。该岭在今同岭村区域隐入地下，其地下结构据《水经注》记载为地下河流分水口。北水汇入汝河，南水流向沙河，溢聚地表部分，形成源泉故称湛源，也就是平顶山的母亲河湛河的源头。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562920670239434.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">湛河源历史悠久，文化底蕴深厚，西汉末年，光武帝刘秀在此留下了许多传说，湛源泉、乌龙泉、白龙泉、马蹄泉、马跑泉等典故，流传至今。湛河源因水土涵养好，水质清澈甘甜，因此，自古以来，此地都有种植莲藕习惯。据民间传说，宋徽宗年间，此地莲藕被钦定为御膳贡品，该区域被称为北方的小江南。</span></p><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562920671640778.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">“采莲南塘秋，莲花过人头，低头弄莲子，莲子清如水”自古农历六月二十四日是莲花生日，各方游客结伴前往湛河源莲花湿地景区划船赏莲，和莲花共度节日。即时，这里微风拂面，莲香阵阵，莲花娇艳欲滴，鱼戏莲叶间，鸟翔荷塘上，形成鸟唱莲舞鱼游的天然美景。</span><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562920795855617.jpg\" title=\"1562920795855617.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>','','','','3,5',1,'1562920823','平顶山市宝丰县杨庄镇东五环与平宝路交叉口东 ',50,0,0.00,0.00),(37,5,12,'七彩沙河水上乐园','轻松舒畅','AAA','上午10点-晚上9点30','1000','3000','2000','/uploads/20190714/b6a57ecbdba51473e2a9e5acaefd7684.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190714/b55ef4f72de6fbe7e24d58e6ce4ad708.jpg','<p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">七彩沙河水上乐园于2015年10月投资兴建，目前已累计投资1.3亿元。建成了我市规模最大的水上乐园，河南省首家中原神汤漂浮馆，目前已形成集农业休闲、旅游观光、文化表演、民俗体育健身为一体的综合性园区。2018年被评定为3A景区，并多次举办大型文化综艺活动及民俗体育赛事，已列入我市重点文化企业。</span></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562920990251833.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"/></span></a><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-size: 12px;\"></a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; display: inline !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">主要景点详细介绍：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px;\"></strong></span></p><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">桃园观赏区、开心农场体验区、绿水游乐区、民俗体育文化区域、不同的区域、享受不同的乐趣、让广大旅游爱好者体验民风、瓜果采摘、水上游乐等各种娱乐项目！<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">常年举办的特色活动：</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"></strong><br/></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">园区不定期举行垂钓大赛、摩托车接力赛、在特定节日推出各种特色活动：如民俗文化暨彩灯嘉年华</span></p><p><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; font-family: \" helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\"></a></p>','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">主要游览线路：<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">停车场-神汤漂浮馆-水上乐园-游艇码头-沿河健身跑道-垂钓基地-桃园观赏区-停车场</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">线路指南：<br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">七彩沙河水上乐园位于河南省平顶山市开源路南段沙河南岸、距平顶山南高速路口1公里，叶县北高速口西2公里、交通便利。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190712/1562921196387493.jpg\" title=\"1562921196387493.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20190707093953.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">长按识别关注 让旅行变得更简单</span></p>','2,3,4',1,'1562921217','平顶山市叶县九龙办事处韩奉村 ',50,0,0.00,0.00),(39,5,9,'画眉谷景区','优秀','AAAA级','8:00-18:00','500','800','400','/uploads/20190715/dee6720ed15b8630a5b67eea371645c1.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190715/98b17c258d92bfec7f58b80c9f426f07.jpg','<p>画眉谷景区，植被茂密，景色优美，自然风光迷人；景区内潭瀑成串，象连缀起来的珍珠熠熠生辉。有崇山峻岭环伺，有悬崖深谷耸峙，小溪清澈，飞瀑直倾，如轻柔的耳语倾诉，又似滔滔不绝激昂的表白：高山流水的音韵铿锵。曲径通幽，有湖光山色映照，共天光云影徘徊；鸟语花香，看龙飞凤舞祥瑞，令驻足留连叹观！好一派田园风光，山水画廊！画眉鸟、画眉谷，天地大美中的灵秀化身！</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190717/1563327812804945.png\" title=\"1563327812804945.png\" alt=\"图片1.png\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190717/1563327836975904.png\" title=\"1563327836975904.png\" alt=\"图片2.png\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">画眉谷景区位于平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇四道河村，总面积99平方公里。景区始建于 2002 年 11 月，2004 年 4 月正式接待游客，2007年 12 月被批准为国家AAA级旅游景区，2011年晋升为国家AAAA级旅游景区，集景区自然观光、休闲度假、拓展、会展培训，漂流避暑、娱乐食宿为一体，很好地满足了游客食宿行、游购娱的基本需求。在市场上有着良好服务口碑及品牌美誉度，是一张平顶山旅游的亮丽名片，吸引着八方游客纷至沓来！</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190717/1563327905725260.png\" title=\"1563327905725260.png\" alt=\"图片3.png\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190717/1563327916168651.png\" title=\"1563327916168651.png\" alt=\"图片4.png\"/>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">主要景点详细介绍：</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">1、游山玩水，娱乐休闲区：设有诸多参与互动性项目，在景区入口到杜鹃湖之间，以嬉水、游乐为主；</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">2、瀑布红石峡区：以小溪水、瀑布、高峡平湖、环球飞车表演观赏为主；</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">3、原始森林区：以六叠瀑布、玻璃桥、悬崖栈道、观景台，及原始森林杜鹃花海的流星观赏为主。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">常年举办的特色活动：</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">歌舞音乐狂欢节、篝火烟花晚会周周举办。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">主要游览线路：</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">1、亲水步道线路：沿溪流、湖、潭，溯源而上，止六叠瀑布、玻璃桥栈道、观景台，顺滑道而下；</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\">2、在景区停车场，乘坐观光车至红石峡区域，没红石瀑布往上走，到六叠瀑布、观光台，然后坐滑道下行，走杜鹃湖乘快艇下山。</p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190717/1563327927330152.png\" title=\"1563327927330152.png\" alt=\"图片5.png\"/></p><p><br/></p>','112.33143','33.802358','','3,4,5,7',1,'1563158464',' 河南省平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇四道河村画眉谷景区（311国道旁边）',50,0,0.00,0.00),(40,5,9,'尧山风景名胜区','优秀','AAAAA级','08:00--18:00','1000','2500','1500','/uploads/20190718/9bbb0409ea64c57d26d8acca54ecbd43.jpg',NULL,'/uploads/20190718/fc65b4b3f1b6ea8ebcf8751cc4d7cfea.jpg','<p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a>尧山风景名胜区是国家级风景名胜区、国家5A级旅游景区、国家生态旅游示范区、国家地质公园、国家标准化服务示范单位。位于河南省平顶山市鲁山县，属山岳型自然风景名胜区，主峰玉皇顶海拔2153.3米，景区总面积268平方公里。尧山雄踞中原，既有北国山岳的雄伟峻拔，也不乏南方山水的钟灵毓秀。景区内奇峰、怪石、飞瀑、温泉、山花、红叶、溪潭、云海、原始森林、珍禽异兽及众多人文景观构成了完整的风景体系。专家评价具有“华山之险、峨嵋之峻、张家界之美、黄山之秀”，集“雄、险、秀、奇、幽”于一体，是旅游观光、避暑疗养、科研探险、寻幽觅奇的理想场所。</a></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;\"><a><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190718/1563443979359781.jpg\" title=\"1563443979359781.jpg\" alt=\"26.jpg\"/></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a>尧山峰奇石怪，尤以象形山石著称，像人、似兽的山石美不胜收，且常有云雾相伴，变幻无穷。如石人、大将军、观音送子、凤凰台等，可谓天然雕像馆。景区森林密布，覆盖率达95%，大片原始森林郁郁葱葱，千年古木随处可见。景区瀑长涧深，九曲瀑涡旋相连，银线瀑（瘦瀑）一线通天，造型奇特，令人叹为观止。尧山四季风光别致，春天鸟语花香，绿映溪吟；夏季云雾缭绕，飞瀑欢唱；秋日满山红遍，层林尽染；冬季银妆素裹，林海雪原。</a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;\"><a><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190718/1563443993753903.jpg\" title=\"1563443993753903.jpg\" alt=\"27.jpg\"/></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a><br/></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a>尧山以尧帝裔孙刘累祭祖立尧祠于此得名，文化底蕴深厚，是刘姓的发源地，战国时伟大思想家墨子的故里。尧山交通便捷，郑州至尧山高速公路、二广高速公路可直达景区。国道311、207。景区紧临焦枝铁路，从北京、上海、广州、重庆、成都、宜昌、怀化、无锡、南京等地均有始发列车经停鲁山火车站。景区内服务设施齐全，有尧山、石人、红枫三条索道和号称“天下第一滑”的2600米花岗岩滑道。尧山脚下的温泉度假酒店、休闲农家乐等可满足多层次游客的需求。</a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a><br/></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;\"><a><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190718/1563444004346228.jpg\" title=\"1563444004346228.jpg\" alt=\"28.jpg\"/></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"/></a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a>目前尧山景区已成为拥有国家级风景名胜区、国家5A级旅游区、国家文明服务示范窗口、国家地质公园、国家级尧山文化旅游服务业标准化试点单位、河南省文明风景旅游区、河南省服务名牌、省级卫生先进单位等多项国家和省级荣誉称号的景区。</a></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><a>尧山是大自然的造化，身临其境，方知其美、其绝。尧山正以奇颜秀貌欢迎八方宾朋！</a></p><p><br/></p>','112.307941','33.735198','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em;\"><a helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">常年举办的特色活动：</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\"></strong></span></a></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em;\"><a helvetica=\"\" color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); max-width: 100%;\">尧山山花节4月中旬-6月上旬；尧山红叶节10月份</span></a></p><p><br/></p>','3,4,5,7',1,'1563443832','河南省平顶山市鲁山县尧山镇西竹园村',1,1,1500.00,100.00);

#
# Structure for table "ddsc_spot_city"
